Definitely a fan. I can't wait to try more of their stuff!", 'date': '2013-08-26 16:18:22', 'user': {'name': 'Tamara', 'review_count': 46, 'yelping_since': '2010-01-25 19:53:12', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.84, 'fans': 2}}
