Then for desserts they have an amazing selection of gelatos and cakes!", 'date': '2021-07-10 02:14:46', 'user': {'name': 'Harris', 'review_count': 18, 'yelping_since': '2009-07-27 02:58:42', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.5, 'fans': 1}}
[R20] {'review_id': 'RlmugF_uQ5g7-PLO7q4jRA', 'user_id': 'ouIyrwwOPt2cG3svK1_QWA', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': 'As the only US outpost of a Roman chain, we had high expectations. The pizza was great- crispy crust, excellent sauces. The dessert case is stunning & both the strawberry marscapone confection & the chocolate mouse were delightful. The service was also very warm & helpful. Quick too. 
Recommend.', 'date': '2021-07-05 18:21:02', 'user': {'name': 'Liesl', 'review_count': 70, 'yelping_since': '2015-08-26 19:16:22', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.89, 'fans': 0}}
[R21] {'review_id': 'UCrbAtBXyOagMN4UhDnIKw', 'user_id': 'OZLQdl_796gZY6KNKiDOzQ', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Went here for lunch with a friend/family. Decided to eat inside. Server was very nice and quick. We ordered Cacio e Pepe fried gnocchi,2 pizza (margarita and roasted pork). Gnocchi and Pizzas were very good.  for my taste (I tried to eat low sodium) the roasted pork was salted but it was delicious. There were square pizza, 4 moderate size slices. We also had gelato and pastry (I had a kinder gelato and apple tart). I didn't like neither. I had way better gelato with more flavor and the apple tart with almond cream was tasteless as well. I certainly will try this place again for the pizza. The only issue is parking around the area, a few parking garages but very expensive at the time we went. I was able to find parking on the street. (Sorry forgot to take pics of the food).", 'date': '2021-06-20 01:34:59', 'user': {'name': 'Dayana', 'review_count': 42, 'yelping_since': '2014-11-23 16:28:38', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.93, 'fans': 0}}
[R22] {'review_id': 'lBzApXjAHVv0HMwkBobBgQ', 'user_id': '4lqWX0UVNXDtDBzaS3cCxw', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'What a beautiful place! The restaurant and bar is both very clean and very pretty. The pizza was absolutely delicious and prepared quickly! The staff was very patient while I was overwhelmed with all of the options!', 'date': '2021-06-09 19:43:24', 'user': {'name': 'Kevin', 'review_count': 22, 'yelping_since': '2021-06-08 05:23:56', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.64, 'fans': 0}}
[R23] {'review_id': 'fnI_nnGxmSBmUgLcDMKtFA', 'user_id': 'j0zF0eXkyrLitSvw8WklEg', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "My husband and I are riding this experience at 5 stars for several reasons. First when I called to request a reservation, I was politely greeting and not kept on hold long. Then when we arrived we didn't wait more than 2min to be seated and we were able to choose which table we wanted to sit at that our waitress was serving. I got the Spicy Shrimp Fra Diavolo and it was delicious! There was a perfect ratio of spicy tomato sauce to fresh homemade fettuccine , and the flavors were rival to the best Italian food I've ever had. There was plenty of shrimp in the dish, not skimpy like other places. My husband had a pizza and they were very accommodating to his specific request as he can be a picky eater especially when it comes to pizza. I was so happy they did not take offense to his order. He enjoyed it very much. I also want to note that the place was very clean, even the bathroom, which surprised me because there were plenty of people in the restaurant and I would have thought it may be neglected since I didn't see a lot of staff, but it was nice. I would definitely return here next time we visit PA.", 'date': '2021-06-06 05:17:24', 'user': {'name': 'Alicia', 'review_count': 39, 'yelping_since': '2014-11-19 17:59:33', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.08, 'fans': 0}}
[R24] {'review_id': 's6trFzeenMGOHXCbxDrzDw', 'user_id': 'BtdqTErMCjvrQxKmBlJ7Uw', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I've really only been here for the gelato, but I love it! It's a nice refreshing treat on a hot day that isn't as heavy as all the ice cream around town. I've had the Limone (lemon) a few times, and occasionally get something chocolatey (like Desire, which if I recall is a vanilla base with chocolate cherry or raspberry mix?) I'm never disappointed. Pre-pandemic they would give samples so you could try all of the flavors before you chose one for your purchase but I don't think they offer that anymore.

I always say I'll come back to try the pizza but who knows if I'll ever get around to it. The gelato is worth it on its own, though!", 'date': '2021-05-31 22:30:51', 'user': {'name': 'Tricia', 'review_count': 250, 'yelping_since': '2015-09-22 18:42:36', 'elite': '2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.12, 'fans': 14}}
[R25] {'review_id': 'rFHWCMqLf514Bz9Wg5Tx7A', 'user_id': 'hImphCrKdXy4rYj7TSZRgw', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I wish I could give it a ZERO. I have ordered pizza and gelato from here in the past. Today I had a limited time for lunch and I ORDERED a pizza for pick-up because I wanted it to be fresh. The ones they have in the display sit out there for a while.

Anyway I picked up the pizza, didn't open it until I got home. In the first place it was barely warm, but I'll forgive that. When I opened it up it was BURNT. I thought it was just the corners but the entire crust was burnt underneath. I will NEVER order or buy anything from this restaurant again. I cannot believe that they would SELL this. It must have been a reject that they were going to throw out. Normally I would have returned it for a refund, but I would have been late for work had I done so. 

The gelato is good, but I'll never be back. I can go to the other restaurant on Chestnut and get gelato.", 'date': '2021-04-21 18:59:38', 'user': {'name': 'Lucero', 'review_count': 43, 'yelping_since': '2010-03-27 21:03:34', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.47, 'fans': 4}}
[R26] {'review_id': 'Iyg32aVITXJpG5WJ_LOvtQ', 'user_id': 'h5nKyARNo0jEhAj7nDZjdg', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "If only ten stars were possible. I was working the first evening we got to Philadelphia. My son decided pizza was on the menu and they went to get it. I am so glad they picked Alice. I feel gipped that we have such awful pizza where we live now that I've had this. We had the veggie and margherita pizza. After, I enjoyed gelato. So tasty.", 'date': '2021-04-18 16:23:27', 'user': {'name': 'Christi', 'review_count': 139, 'yelping_since': '2015-09-28 17:36:00', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.22, 'fans': 3}}
[R27] {'review_id': 'R2bpTSW4gQFVrVXHv_FLhg', 'user_id': 'GvF2XPPJYQDl5u7eHbLa0g', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'WARNING - not open until 10pm. Walked in on a a Thursday night at 9:18pm and the kitchen had "already been closed for a while" and they had already done last call for the bar. Looked delicious and was disappointed in the false advertising. Update your hours if you're only open until 9pm', 'date': '2021-04-09 01:21:21', 'user': {'name': 'Birdie', 'review_count': 26, 'yelping_since': '2014-07-27 17:23:14', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.5, 'fans': 0}}
[R28] {'review_id': 'Im5bGeNcSTjiodOuQ6dUwA', 'user_id': 'DB8sZjbJ-HTJIk1rBU1oAQ', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "We got take out to eat in our hotel room after a long day of site seeing. The online menu was easy to use. Pizzas were ready on time and hot after our short walk back to the room. We got the personal sized Margherita pizza, which had four large slices, a crispy crust and the perfect amount of cheese (shredded vs Buffalo mozzarella circles) and tomato sauce. Our second pick was the Casio e Pepi that had a thin crispy crust and rich creamy sauce with black pepper and cheese. Very good, yet rich. They also had a a wide selection selection of gelato, which we didn't try,but that looked delicious.", 'date': '2021-04-04 17:16:19', 'user': {'name': 'Ashley', 'review_count': 28, 'yelping_since': '2016-05-02 22:49:30', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.82, 'fans': 0}}
