Try this place. You won't be sad.", 'date': '2021-03-16 23:32:19', 'user': {'name': 'Bill', 'review_count': 23, 'yelping_since': '2010-08-06 04:12:16', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.5, 'fans': 1}}
[R30] {'review_id': '501Pdyzbr3hb7LYf-3nHeg', 'user_id': 'ZS85bkvRejJaPKMhxfx1GQ', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Best pizza we've had since moving to philly. Very reasonably priced for the quality. Pachino E Buffalo was amazing!", 'date': '2021-03-07 02:58:46', 'user': {'name': 'Jennifer', 'review_count': 13, 'yelping_since': '2009-09-08 02:37:31', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.08, 'fans': 2}}
[R31] {'review_id': 'dNcJ1GVHltCgTi5uUh0iCw', 'user_id': 'e33l3ucOBsdsb8jyegZVVQ', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "This place used to be better when first opened. I lived in nearby apartment so I know for sure how they have changed the ingredients on their pizza especially the mushroom pizza. They used portobello mushroom  before but now it's just regular mushroom. Its definitely a big minus. I hope they will switch back. Otherwise pizza is still good.", 'date': '2021-01-26 18:53:32', 'user': {'name': 'Iris', 'review_count': 6, 'yelping_since': '2014-04-21 19:08:59', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R32] {'review_id': 'xU0Y1Ji5JqO9zz2t8RQ7mg', 'user_id': 'dI_ohX8Sn8u7N7IcvxwQXw', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 1, 'text': 'pleasantly surprised how good the food was .
the "personal "size pizza was really large enough for two to share , once you can agree on what type ! many fresh ,healthy choices as well as plain out just yummy...we had the pork, pulled and with bbq sauce as well as the eggplant ,tomatoes, mozzarella cheese choice ...
the crust is crunchy ,perfect !
our party of 5 included a teenager who chowed down on the meatballs (side dish) ,as well the fried dough with sauce .happy kid ,no easy task .
the coffee is delicious. absolutely the best I have had in town ,pre covid included .
we ended the meal with the cookie sample plate ..
great cookies ,biscotti, traditional and not overly sweet .
the manager ,Shawn was helpful ,and personable,and not in that sappy fakey way you get with some establishment. he was lovely to talk to ,genuine .
I would give alice 5 stars except for the broken window we were seated near .long story short apparently some road work caused a pebble to crack the window ,which was "fixed " temporarily by securing the outside of the large window with plywood ,but not the inside .
my teenage grandson and daughter both sat up straight  in their chairs  and ....heard the crack get larger ...
no one was hurt ,but we were lucky .
the manager was apologetic and earnest .
appreciated that .
definitely will return ,so much to try on the menu !', 'date': '2021-01-18 21:54:06', 'user': {'name': 'Lolly', 'review_count': 26, 'yelping_since': '2020-04-14 01:17:34', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.67, 'fans': 2}}
[R33] {'review_id': 'a11BkY90Jae_q4TSFqMy8g', 'user_id': 'ZCVEZmTB_StK-UXA3WPVlQ', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Solid. I got the lunch combo of the Suppli Al Telefano and slice of Margarita pizza. The suppli al telefano is a rice croquet with mozzarella in the center and a beef/veal ragu in with the rice. It was lighter than expected (fried food can sometimes be heavy/dense) this was not but it would have been better if it came with a small ramekin of their tomato sauce to dip it in as the acid would have complimented and brought out the flavor more. I suspect when dining in or outside this may be how they are served as an app but they should include with the take out order combo. The pizza is square cut (I got a corner slice! score!) is very delicate with a crisp crust and nice balance of cheese to sauce. I also splurged for an Isgro cannoli because how can one not? All in all a very tasty lunch!', 'date': '2020-12-23 18:31:47', 'user': {'name': 'Zanna', 'review_count': 523, 'yelping_since': '2008-01-10 14:09:37', 'elite': '2008,2009,2010,2011,2012,2013,2014,2015,2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.56, 'fans': 73}}
[R34] {'review_id': 'xmmirUyCHMx34kjXHpQwGw', 'user_id': 'UBiJ0YhkHZWM1CuUTy-2qA', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I've had pizza at probably 50+ places in the city over the last 10 years. Alice Pizza's pizza is the best, in my opinion. Whether a speciality pizza or regular, they're both 10/10 in flavor. This place also has the most delicious desserts and coffee selections (lattes, etc). Dined here during the pandemic in their outdoor seating area. Must try for lunch or dinner - you'll be back, I promise!", 'date': '2020-12-12 20:18:28', 'user': {'name': 'Rachael', 'review_count': 151, 'yelping_since': '2014-10-22 18:06:20', 'elite': '20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.29, 'fans': 1}}
[R35] {'review_id': '3SntHRDBKzKjxptp9WvC4A', 'user_id': 'wDDDAueA098iH3W3Y1MuOQ', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "It's the perfect pizza. I usually don't crave pizza but I constantly crave Alice. My go-to is the spicy salami but my fiance love the spicy tomato. Both are excellent choices!", 'date': '2020-12-08 21:38:58', 'user': {'name': 'J Ng', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2016-05-08 23:44:50', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R36] {'review_id': 'RQYPyyJiXWkYChcWpfDZ0Q', 'user_id': 'LA4DxijAdk04kf24k0_7fg', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I love this place's pizza. I started going here because I missed Rione earlier in this pandemic when it was closed but this place stands out on its own. I get the four cheese mushroom pizza which is my favorite. If you really like rosemary there's also a potato rosemary pizza. My mom enjoys the margherita pizza when she visits. We usually get 2-4 square slices per person for two people and two drinks, and we generally have a cost of 14-18$ because they charge you by weight. They will heat it up for you if you ask, but I will note it still is quite tasty at room temp. They have been very nice and have always wrapped/packed my slices nicely.

I haven't tried their gelato (i would have to eat it before the pizza for takeout) but it looks good along with their dessert spread. This pizza tastes like what I had in Italy, pizza al taglio. I prefer this type of pizza to say Neapolitan style personally.", 'date': '2020-12-04 22:57:47', 'user': {'name': 'Elise', 'review_count': 144, 'yelping_since': '2011-09-03 05:58:49', 'elite': '2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.41, 'fans': 9}}
[R37] {'review_id': 'QVJLDVKvP--cWNmUC60lfA', 'user_id': 'rxgoHeIus7ES4cGrg8DUqQ', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Visited this restaurant for dinner a couple of times and got some drinks. The drinks were very reasonably price I think. Both of the pizzas were very delicious. One was a margherita pizza and the other was a amatriciana pizza. I would definitely recommend. They have heating lamps for outside dining. Our waiter wore a mask and they have sanitizing stations inside the restaurant.', 'date': '2020-12-04 02:56:59', 'user': {'name': 'Tashalee', 'review_count': 183, 'yelping_since': '2014-11-18 14:55:26', 'elite': '2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.19, 'fans': 35}}
[R38] {'review_id': '0MWFjJdeoCDmCH8cI6ugzw', 'user_id': 'y8bw--UQIOI8yNcCfzynTw', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Alice Pizza you are most certainly magnificent, I had a lovely experience here yesterday. Very cute spot with great prices and good choices. Absolutely yummy! Every single thing is super fresh! All of the staff are really pleasant - you certainly feel welcome and taken care of. Certainly will come back to Alice Pizza always.', 'date': '2020-11-02 12:49:19', 'user': {'name': 'Cynthia', 'review_count': 149, 'yelping_since': '2020-10-18 23:42:10', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.8, 'fans': 1}}
[R39] {'review_id': 'tb1fLmEW92UvFa6E8RwtGg', 'user_id': 'rn7waL3tAu6qoB7RGNzuKg', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Finally got to check out this place that's right across the street from my place! We ordered the Diavola Pizza, Calamari Fritti, and Cotoletta Romana. The pizza was so delicious and so flavorful, with plenty of sauce and toppings! The thin square pizzas are my favorite kinds to eat, and Alice Pizza does the Roman style pizzas so well. The calamari was lightly fried (which I like), and chicken cutlet was very filling. Sadly, I didn't get to try any dessert this time, but I'll definitely be back to try it next time! I'm so glad I found a nice pizza spot to satisfy my pizza cravings!", 'date': '2020-10-31 16:36:28', 'user': {'name': 'Jung', 'review_count': 91, 'yelping_since': '2012-07-10 04:03:32', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.41, 'fans': 5}}
[R40] {'review_id': 'M8kG6SGilbS74rIf0Qt28w', 'user_id': 'zwsAA-LTMBQlheFLO2HRCA', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': 'The desserts and the ice creams are great, although the ice cream was a bit too sweet for our liking. Loved the chocolate-raspberry mousse, though!', 'date': '2020-10-28 23:11:34', 'user': {'name': 'Alexandra', 'review_count': 184, 'yelping_since': '2015-10-16 20:10:22', 'elite': '2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.77, 'fans': 9}}
[R41] {'review_id': '1DFj275BJ6ije2_h0e6hJQ', 'user_id': '02j6aTPZVzzYdHeJ-JIT5w', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Alice Pizza never fails to satisfy my pizza cravings. The crust is so buttery and delicious!!', 'date': '2020-10-21 04:38:17', 'user': {'name': 'Perry', 'review_count': 8, 'yelping_since': '2011-11-29 00:32:50', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.75, 'fans': 0}}
[R42] {'review_id': 'tBSxpDihHoNB9rX0enH3Vg', 'user_id': 'B_SBNlvZ46mzV4c6yqVBMA', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I love Alice. It was my go-to for a quick post-show bite before COVID and today I got a personal pizza for takeout for the first time -- it was great! I got the Quattro Stagioni since that had never been available for slice orders (all I'd ever done before).", 'date': '2020-10-19 04:03:44', 'user': {'name': 'Laura', 'review_count': 28, 'yelping_since': '2019-10-09 22:55:33', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.7, 'fans': 0}}
[R43] {'review_id': '4P4g7ne_a7G8G7RUztJi2g', 'user_id': '94BPeyvx0Ow447J-R7nxYA', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The pizza is delicious each time we go. The diavola (spicy pepperoni), bufala Margherita, and fungi quatro (mushroom) are all amazing. We've only done pizza takeout so don't know about the restaurant experience. The desserts we've tried were not great (cannoli and Napoleon), but we'll keep coming back for the pizza.", 'date': '2020-10-17 01:08:29', 'user': {'name': 'James', 'review_count': 26, 'yelping_since': '2012-12-04 05:56:48', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.5, 'fans': 0}}
[R44] {'review_id': 'DETqFJCVMNki85N6R_leiA', 'user_id': 'HVQKFDi-vZbawtmLMq3ZOw', 'business_id': 'VSDdUwXktnvL_O0meKv7MQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I went to one of the Alice locations in Italy years ago, and I'm so glad they opened up stateside!! The pizza is by weight (just like in Italy) and it's amazing. The tomato pizza was my favorite, though the porcini mushrooms and sausage was also great. I need to come back to try the gelato and tiramisu!", 'date': '2020-10-11 14:40:36', 'user': {'name': 'Gab', 'review_count': 2422, 'yelping_since': '2010-06-12 13:05:15', 'elite': '2015,2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.2, 'fans': 178}}
