[R33] {'review_id': 'hiy2ibQis4yJZmVAVY8x6w', 'user_id': 'e6heoqu1EnKkaNFbf1N7CQ', 'business_id': 'B5eJm8A4eiuPLW5C6l75dQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 4, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 2, 'text': "Came here for a 30th birthday after hours and had such a great time with a few friends. I never been here during the day but I highly suggest making a booking after hours and you can try ANYTHING you want in the store for approximately 2 hours (except the raw foods - like bacon.. if only they could cook it!). It comes with a price but its SO worth it and so much fun! You can be fancy schmancy and bring your own wine/beer too :)

