[R21] {'review_id': '_66-TN3yWtibB31gIbI5pg', 'user_id': 'JHR4sNDbgDFJvLRxA7Gs-Q', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'I gave them four stars because this establishment is very transparent in what you get: a college student centered, late night pizza. The cheese pizza was pretty good, a little undercooked, but again this place serves its purpose. Cheap and pretty good.', 'date': '2019-05-17 06:20:03', 'user': {'name': 'Christian', 'review_count': 16, 'yelping_since': '2019-05-14 17:43:22', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.33, 'fans': 1}}
[R22] {'review_id': 'bYwBtacfAOz0xHUIIK1DXQ', 'user_id': '37bjmw5F6FwMnaTRsrEhYg', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': 'With three stars, it might seem like this will be a bad review, but I actually love and regularly order Allegro pizza - it\'s just important to have the right expectations going in. Allegro is good for "college pizza" - late night, not-much-else-is-open, dependable kind of pizza. I usually get a large cheese, and every single time have had to re-cook it in my oven at home because the dough is still soft. Once re-cooked, it\'s great! They\'re really generous with the cheese, and the crust is thin without being insubstantial. So if you want some solid late-night pizza, and don\'t mind the extra 10 min of recooking, Allegro is a good choice.', 'date': '2019-05-16 19:41:10', 'user': {'name': 'Liz', 'review_count': 74, 'yelping_since': '2019-05-14 05:00:28', 'elite': '20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.59, 'fans': 2}}
[R23] {'review_id': 'TkfJO8CLSwysSYTAkwhcwA', 'user_id': 'mA5kFLWiuNRfNB81m4HsYg', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Allegro pizza!!! This is definitely the place to go if you want shitty pizza and shitty service. They have the worst pizza and service ever. Please save your money and go somewhere else. They are not worthy of my one star that I have to give on my review.', 'date': '2019-04-21 04:32:33', 'user': {'name': 'Sophie', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2019-04-21 04:32:30', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 1.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R24] {'review_id': 'KopPAjy-CbwhcbXG7dqT2A', 'user_id': '-PHhewouMe4OcObjdqBWAA', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Oh Allegro. I've had it so many times that at this point, I can recognize the smell of it from anywhere. The pizza itself is so oily that you can use 1-2 napkins to wipe it off beforehand. It looks and tastes like it was designed for drunk college students to munch on after a long night. Don't come here if you don't have a good reason to.", 'date': '2019-04-17 21:47:26', 'user': {'name': 'Alfred', 'review_count': 186, 'yelping_since': '2017-11-15 23:06:18', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.03, 'fans': 14}}
[R25] {'review_id': 'dT5EZrbuft4qEkmWeneWXg', 'user_id': 'td-PD_jhDK6TlME6sdxFMw', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Ordered delivery for two pizzas and a side of mozzarella sticks. One large 16 inch bbq pizza and one regular 14 inch veg pizza. Received a wrong sized pie. Called the restaurant immediately to see if they could correct the mistake. Gentleman by the name of Valentino claimed to be the manager for "5yrs without a problem"  cursed me out and hung up on me after I asked him for his name repeatedly and if he could correct the mistake. Contacted grubhub\'s customer care service and I was told by Grubhub the restaurant would not send the correct item and that at the moment they were not able to refund me at that I would be contacted by via email. My order was 59dollars. They took my money, got my order wrong, refused to correct their mistake, cursed at me, and hung up on me. I will be pursuing my refund. Allegro\'s you can expect to hear from in the immediate future.', 'date': '2019-03-16 08:34:08', 'user': {'name': 'Freddy', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2017-11-26 13:01:46', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 1.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R26] {'review_id': 'wR-_wEvdyJnJDugTMey7dg', 'user_id': 'bEadB1h4l7kSU9ApZFTeHg', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Lots of reviews saying this is a good drunk-pizza place. No - it's much better than that. We order delivery from here a couple of times a month and the stromboli is EPIC. So good. And their salads are luscious, fresh and generously-portioned. Delivery from this place is a go-to for us...we recommend!", 'date': '2019-03-04 14:39:53', 'user': {'name': 'Amy', 'review_count': 29, 'yelping_since': '2013-02-26 23:08:11', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.48, 'fans': 0}}
[R27] {'review_id': 'JRLwL_pKRnsUQNXwDQBXug', 'user_id': '8622sgILqHspzSs_WE75Pg', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': '...allegro just lost a long time, steady customer.   over the last several months, they\'ve screwed up my order almost every time.   this last time, they added the extra bonus of blaming me for the screw up.   about a week ago, i ordered a large extra cheese pizza and a 20 oz. coke, the pizza came to me with 1/3 of the cheese slid off of the pizza and congealed in the corner of the box, and they forgot my coke.   when i called to complain, the young lady on the phone told me; "this happens sometimes when the pizza is hot"   ...uh, what???   ...seriously???   ...that\'s the "explanation" you\'re going with?   ...anyway, she offered to credit me for my next order, which i accepted.   last night, i ordered a pizza and a sprite, when i asked if they had my credit on file, the man on the phone said; "yes, i see a credit for $10", which was odd, because my previous order total was $20 and change, the man\'s reply was "i don\'t know what to tell you, buddy, i can only see what is on the computer"   ...unwilling to argue over $10, i placed the order ...2 hours later, i called an asked if my order was coming any time soon, he told me "we tried to deliver, but you never answer your phone, we call many times", which was a lie, my phone was sitting in front of me on the coffee table the entire time (after he said that, i even had my GF test call me just to be sure my ringer was on) ...the man on the phone became argumentative with me, insisting it was my fault my order did\'nt get delivered, i cut him off and just asked them to bring my food ...another 40 minutes later, the driver shows up with the cold pizza, and a diet dr. pepper (i asked for a sprite)   ...this is merely the most recent of screw ups, but i kept giving them chances because i\'ve been going there since i was a teen, they do have decent food, they\'re close to the house, and up until recent years, the customer service has been good ...but i am done with allegro, they will get no more of my money.', 'date': '2019-02-16 04:08:51', 'user': {'name': 'Nerdy_Hercules', 'review_count': 12, 'yelping_since': '2014-11-08 02:08:23', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.67, 'fans': 0}}
[R28] {'review_id': '4hbk_wEEe8urIInh0Z4vhw', 'user_id': 'tNED5YZZkosm0wRLk6VrFw', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "By far the most mediocre pizza I've ever had. If you are on campus and perhaps drunk, then it's a great spot. Optimal drunk food. However, if you're sober, prepare for a usually long line, and a super mediocre, slightly stale slice of pizza.", 'date': '2019-01-31 01:48:52', 'user': {'name': 'Joe', 'review_count': 70, 'yelping_since': '2014-10-29 00:31:24', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.18, 'fans': 6}}
