[R30] {'review_id': 'AW84BYcn9Qki9LXa9DfkrQ', 'user_id': 'yK-2oGtDxm8XLg7hVVdQ-Q', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Allegro was a pretty good place for a cheesesteak. I mean, it wasn't as great as the secret cheesesteaks on other menus from pizza joints around the Philly area, but it is better than the tourist traps. It is definitely a hangout for cops in the area and students wanting a slice of pizza or sandwich. They have a good beer selection too. Make sure you ask for the fried onions on your cheesesteak or you won't get them.", 'date': '2018-12-24 21:03:13', 'user': {'name': 'Brian', 'review_count': 151, 'yelping_since': '2011-04-23 12:29:57', 'elite': '2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.3, 'fans': 15}}
[R31] {'review_id': 'LpWhWKWqU2ww5YC4hc72Mw', 'user_id': 'ctqtCB5x0whmy8jFLkVF5Q', 'business_id': 'bSWL0YxfawjS03_g2kgujA', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I have enjoyed their food for years working overnights in University City, especially because of how late they deliver (3:30 AM on Friday and Saturday), their location, and that I'm not able to leave the building until 7:00 AM. Saturday morning around 3:00 AM, I place an online order. Confirmation e-mail estimates delivery around 3:34 AM. I wait another 15-20 minutes past that to call because I am busy helping clients. I call twice to confirm my order and the phone rings several times before it hangs up. No one called to say they were on their way or that they could or could not fulfill my order, so now my card's charged and I received no food. If their hours changed in general or because of the holidays, they should have reached out to me. I had to wait to call them the following morning to get refunded. They were apologetic and handled it, but it was disappointing considering I did enjoy their service and menu previously.", 'date': '2018-12-22 09:52:51', 'user': {'name': 'Don', 'review_count': 3, 'yelping_since': '2010-04-20 15:49:26', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.67, 'fans': 1}}
