[R3] {'review_id': 'BA1FT2F6ljao8gqkXPW29w', 'user_id': 'Ut6P-CKiz1KLAmaaWP63_g', 'business_id': 'uKAbrDSJJzZliY1Yqu5KxQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': "I visited Scannicchio's Sunday afternoon Nov.14 we were a party of 5, our waitress was  Nikai this was her first week, I must say she did a fantastic job, everything was as ordered, even though my sister wanted to create her own dish, which Nikai had no problem with , it came out just the way she wanted it, although Scannicchio's never disappoints in food or in service...this is a place we visit frequently & will continue to do so...\nNikai is certainly an asset, she is pleasant & personable. & 6", 'date': '2021-11-16 19:26:43', 'user': {'name': 'Joanne', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2015-03-10 11:37:27', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R4] {'review_id': 'thpBaS06HWWkryBha76_Dw', 'user_id': 'kal8gYskg4tq1G0-t9kcmA', 'business_id': 'uKAbrDSJJzZliY1Yqu5KxQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Yes 5 stars. Excellent from the house salad to the escarole and beans. We both had chicken dishes which were excellent as was the penne and gravy. More food than we could eat. Glad I messed up on my flight arrangements so we could try this place. Will go back.', 'date': '2021-08-26 23:35:13', 'user': {'name': 'Heidi', 'review_count': 194, 'yelping_since': '2012-05-16 17:14:07', 'elite': '20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.99, 'fans': 1}}
[R5] {'review_id': 'Hnda0AQUT-m_abdKH-Zm7Q', 'user_id': 'dXTtctMtOAj5xlgfYtlgaQ', 'business_id': 'uKAbrDSJJzZliY1Yqu5KxQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Great little spot on Broad St! BYOB restaurant with huge potions and the food is always amazing. The chicken parm is massive. Vodka sauce has great flavor. Family run place with a great vibe.', 'date': '2021-04-30 00:51:18', 'user': {'name': 'Lauren', 'review_count': 4, 'yelping_since': '2015-02-08 02:44:57', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R6] {'review_id': '9G2q05Fx5-YEw_q5FLgDYA', 'user_id': '__GHy1xxetn0SBqP4b_odA', 'business_id': 'uKAbrDSJJzZliY1Yqu5KxQ', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The other half of the story from my L'Angelo's review - several years ago I was going out on a date and walked into this place several hours before closing. It was right in the middle of dinner hour, actually, and the dinning hall was pack. We were immediately told by the host that the kitchen was closed. It was then, looking around at the sea of White faces who all stopped eating to stare at us, that we realized why we had that awkward experience down the street - they didn't want to serve us because we were Black. It was weird to experience such ugly and open racism right on Broad Street, but here we are, part of a long lineage of Black folks getting denied dinners at restaurants throughout the decades. Hopefully my kids never have to endure something like that.", 'date': '2021-04-04 11:31:43', 'user': {'name': 'John', 'review_count': 33, 'yelping_since': '2009-07-19 13:43:27', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.64, 'fans': 3}}
[R7] {'review_id': 'lRUKSIkHbHe_x2nPbqDo7g', 'user_id': 'lwUa756W1t0jX68St3hPWw', 'business_id': 'uKAbrDSJJzZliY1Yqu5KxQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Absolutely delicious. Amazing service and great people. This place is byob which is a huge plus. Not to mention the food is amazing. Calamari amazing. Arranchini amazing. Tortellini Alfredo amazing. Penna vodka AMAZING !!  Don't waste your time going to any other Italian restaurant in this City. If you can get a reservation here BOOK IT!!!", 'date': '2021-02-12 01:13:08', 'user': {'name': 'Britt', 'review_count': 32, 'yelping_since': '2013-06-11 03:25:27', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.69, 'fans': 0}}
