[R25] {'review_id': 'VIG9oPdJIb3W_jbdfco2Cw', 'user_id': 'RnsGfdux_mwwOEIx-piakA', 'business_id': 'pxmBh8YZ6HLGQfNHvJoHzA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Nomad is great for happy hour, especially with large groups. Came here the other day with a group of ~8 people, and they were able to take a reservation for us with no problem.
 They had a few pizzas on happy hour special special, all with thin and crispy crusts. I had the margarita, which was standard but flavorful. I also tried some of the tomato pie, which had a delicious tomato sauce. They had a variety of sausage-topped pizzas that seemed to be well-received by my friends. 
Docked one star because the prices have increased quite a bit for their happy hour specials (no longer $5 pizzas). But for the taste and convenience, Nomad is a great choice!', 'date': '2019-05-12 22:18:59', 'user': {'name': 'Sanika', 'review_count': 71, 'yelping_since': '2016-03-16 05:12:40', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.31, 'fans': 4}}
[R26] {'review_id': 'G081Wa6MmH5RucrdZqrOHg', 'user_id': 'kh8FA-_QSuTL1U0fygs6Cg', 'business_id': 'pxmBh8YZ6HLGQfNHvJoHzA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Managed to grab a table with a group of friends right after Nomad had opened again after being closed for a private event. The staff was super friendly and nice (they were in the process of cleaning up after the event) and were patient with us even though we changed our idea of where to sit like 3 times (we had the whole place to ourselves and was overwhelmed with where to sit lol!) so extra points for being patient with us lol. A staff member put us in a really great spot near the opened windows so we got a view of the street. It was a beautiful Friday night so people watching was prime.  

Our server was funny, nice, engaging -  over all great energy. We ordered two pizzas (a Margherita pizza and a special pizza), two orders of meatballs and a Caesar salad for the table.The one pizza was from the specials list, it had Chorizo on it, and it was delicious! Me and my friend joked that when we come back, we'll have to order the special Chorizo pizza to ourselves because it was *that* good. I ordered a cocktail which was really good as well! 

We must have gotten in at a good time because it wasn't long before the place started filling up! Based off that, I'm assuming a reservation is needed for this restaurant, which isn't a big deal. 

I will definitely be back - looking forward to it!", 'date': '2019-05-06 20:02:28', 'user': {'name': 'Cayleesi', 'review_count': 15, 'yelping_since': '2015-11-14 23:00:40', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.33, 'fans': 0}}
