[R43] {'review_id': 'QntJwnrCXDEN8l_P5oI3qg', 'user_id': '030xaqW2akhXYFdmOTmEng', 'business_id': 'bchZXVE4feVx4Q5rhIRCGg', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 2, 'text': "I first learned of NY Bagel and Cafe from a coupon insert in the mail, and decided to give it a try since it's in close proximity to my office. I admit I didn't have the highest of expectations beforehand, but was very impressed with the hoagie that I ordered (roast beef & cheddar with spicy mayo). I love that the meal comes with house-made bagel chips (so so much better than ordinary potato chips). The prices here are also super reasonable compared to some of the other lunch options on City Ave. And my order has always been ready by the time I stopped in. Highly recommend!", 'date': '2016-07-18 17:29:36', 'user': {'name': 'Christopher', 'review_count': 200, 'yelping_since': '2010-07-05 02:00:28', 'elite': '2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.27, 'fans': 31}}
[R44] {'review_id': 'kRMMjNc0HkXaIKuFVy9U5g', 'user_id': 'Od2Ev0b92eKrciDJIRVNpQ', 'business_id': 'bchZXVE4feVx4Q5rhIRCGg', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Have eaten inside a couple of time and food is prepped quick.  There wasn't much of a line.  The place itself to get to is inopportune and previous eateries near this location have not succeeded.  \n\nI will say the bagels are good and probably one of the few good non main line establishments.  The salad is a descent size but simple, filling though.  \n\nThe bagel chips I will give a 10 for originality as that is the side that comes with the sandwiches.", 'date': '2016-06-25 00:30:01', 'user': {'name': 'Matt', 'review_count': 552, 'yelping_since': '2010-02-19 04:39:38', 'elite': '2013,2014,2015,2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.86, 'fans': 21}}
