                    + (DATE_DECAY * 0.4) 
                    + (BaseCuisineRisk * 0.6) 
                    + COMPOUND_RISK_INDEX 
                    + (TEMPORAL_TREND * 1.5)
                    + CUISINE_MODIFIER 
                    + (BASELINE_UNCERTAINTY * 0.5)

    SAFETY_MARGIN = Max(0.0, 9.0 - PreliminaryRisk)
    FINAL_RISK_SCORE = PreliminaryRisk - (SAFETY_MARGIN * 0.1)
    ```
