[R4] {'review_id': 'O5Wq-FMoQXnSWo9rTeEDrQ', 'user_id': '9JTvg-ryS1CiLmwph3usCQ', 'business_id': 'k2YJkdLg25xlYjshpeEtkQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Best avocado toast I've ever had, hands down. They do NOT skimp on the avocado here. You can have it topped with egg and cream cheese for a protein- rich breakfast, or have it heaped with arugula and other veggies for something lighter and wholesome. The paninis are really generous too!\n\nThey serve La Colombe coffee and it's always great. They serve their cappuccinos with lots of foam which I personally really like sometimes. When you can sit inside, it's a sunny, cheerful atmosphere. The staff is very friendly!", 'date': '2021-12-04 05:01:22', 'user': {'name': 'Eibhleann', 'review_count': 3, 'yelping_since': '2021-12-04 04:48:05', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R5] {'review_id': 'eDyhqDunVY7UFZAv1nZ79A', 'user_id': 's3IJ26fV1bLk1K0xBiwp9w', 'business_id': 'k2YJkdLg25xlYjshpeEtkQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 1, 'text': "I've only gotten an iced tea from here but I really enjoyed it and honestly, I feel like you can judge a place pretty well on how good their plain black iced tea is! The one thing that i've felt the few times i've been here, and both times it was a random weekday and not crowded, was that it wasn't super welcoming. Like I felt very intimidated walking in there. Maybe it's because all of the staff are standing in a row when you walk in and just stare at you? I guess that's sorta the vibe at most coffee shops but still just wanted to note that if you get nervous ordering make sure you look at the menu and decide beforehand.", 'date': '2021-09-26 14:35:45', 'user': {'name': 'Jennifer', 'review_count': 11, 'yelping_since': '2018-02-20 05:21:41', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.09, 'fans': 0}}
