[R3] {'review_id': 'bGHeDc-8AafY28rG1Exbfw', 'user_id': 'Gjt-uAfqnbjERgolE7KlVA', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I just had the most horrible sandwich I have had in the last decade. I asked for just one thing if the sandwiches were hot. I got a lightly toasted multigrain bread with watery babaganoush leaking from it. Imagine starving and still wanting to throw your food away. The sandwich menu here needs to be killed. It's a cutesy place with coffee and pastries, but sandwiches they make are like my 3 year old makes - Hey I put a bunch of things between bread!", 'date': '2021-12-03 20:16:36', 'user': {'name': 'Ant', 'review_count': 183, 'yelping_since': '2009-04-06 02:31:57', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.26, 'fans': 6}}
[R4] {'review_id': 'KkMvgXsvTQxURAmYFNnLXw', 'user_id': 'bdcjp1w6GdZN3HOQOxE_EA', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I was scouring the city looking for a fresh cup of coffee and when I found the menagerie I was starkly disappointed not only was I rudely treated when I tried to enter the location momentarily adjusting my mask after jogging through the city but then on top of that there was another patron who walked in who is verbally assaulted for not wearing his mask by some guy in a red beanie the guy in the red beanie was so mean so rude honestly I don't understand why you hired him.. save your money and find someone who understands humanity.", 'date': '2021-11-28 16:48:48', 'user': {'name': 'Torry', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2018-07-31 17:51:03', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R5] {'review_id': 'NoSjXMUdc67VZFK1I6Cfvg', 'user_id': 'BZtELQcbVewiBbz8FkN6Kw', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Insanely overrated. A very average latte, pastries are nothing special (like some packaged Little Debbie quality). Visited before 10am so I expected fresher stuff.', 'date': '2021-09-13 13:54:31', 'user': {'name': 'Kristine', 'review_count': 6, 'yelping_since': '2019-01-18 23:11:06', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.71, 'fans': 0}}
[R6] {'review_id': 'GOxrFaUxv2ZsXOtmGbiW5g', 'user_id': 'xiLEwSjb05Bt3-jPRYPFmQ', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The coldbrew was indeed smooth, and affordable compared to NY and LA prices. Paid ~3.50 for a 16 ounce! Only thing I'd change; I asked for water and they said they didn't give out cups of it, only bottles of water. In the 95 degree August heat, this is a bummer.", 'date': '2021-08-25 01:50:14', 'user': {'name': 'GV', 'review_count': 13, 'yelping_since': '2019-10-19 19:52:18', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.29, 'fans': 0}}
[R7] {'review_id': 'QA7AOMDXvIJLWhqn4JO1XA', 'user_id': 'op2c4RQMptf9pi5KoNltWw', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'We stopped there for coffee. The service was great, the place was clean and the food was fresh and delicious! They have a great menu.\nThe food was tasty and the waiter was very warm and friendly.\nThis is a quaint little place with so much charm. The food was very good and generous portions were served. Seating is limited but worth the wait for a table.', 'date': '2021-08-24 08:41:38', 'user': {'name': 'Elijah', 'review_count': 31, 'yelping_since': '2021-08-10 02:38:55', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.36, 'fans': 2}}
[R8] {'review_id': 'ZARgvOCf5jYqwKARCOE8_g', 'user_id': '9lCb0V9FVtvI9qHuZhJmqw', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I met an old friend to catch up with at Menagerie. It was the day that the mask mandates and updates around COVID changed yet again and so there were no tables or chairs to sit inside, but nbd. We ordered our large cold brews with a couple scones and walked over to the park nearby. \n\nBy far the best cold brew coffee I've had outside of the ones I make myself at home! In fact, it was so good that I went back to get another one on my way back home! Staff are friendly and they were practicing all the safety protocols. I'd definitely venture out a bit for this coffee - yes, it's that good!", 'date': '2021-08-13 15:53:17', 'user': {'name': 'Suhee', 'review_count': 334, 'yelping_since': '2012-10-04 23:49:29', 'elite': '2015,2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.76, 'fans': 13}}
[R9] {'review_id': 'Mr5f-SNrJwHl5Tx4IVSGlw', 'user_id': 'oDzRf_NuDKkZKQZVFRW6ng', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Great place in old city to catch up with friends or some work. \nThe coffee was very good, and there's usually a fairly decent amount of selections for pastries and sandwiches. They're nothing special but it's always good to have something to snack on while doing work.\nThe wifi was fairly reliable and there were lots of space, including a big table at the back, although if it's on a busy weekend, you might have to share tables with others. The bathroom was clean and there're quite a few places with outlets in case you plan on staying there for a while. \nOnly complaint is that some of the areas are a bit dark. i'm someone who likes lots of natural light and well-lit spaces when i work, but the dimmer environment definitely has a more homey cozy vibe to it, which others might like.", 'date': '2021-08-05 00:38:47', 'user': {'name': 'Jasmine', 'review_count': 55, 'yelping_since': '2016-07-05 02:31:31', 'elite': '2021', 'average_stars': 3.74, 'fans': 3}}
[R10] {'review_id': '9VQbG7GzeALNg7pSY8QO4w', 'user_id': 'jj7qARHi2gfTZY87v2RQsw', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 8, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 6, 'text': "I really wanted to like this place more because it's cute and the service is friendly, but IMHO, Elixr coffee is too harsh and bitter and the couple of pastries I tried (coffee cake muffin and oatmeal raisin cookies) were just okay. I was here a couple of days in a row on a recent visit to Philly, trying to give it another shot, but stopped coming after the third day", 'date': '2021-08-03 22:40:38', 'user': {'name': 'Bob', 'review_count': 881, 'yelping_since': '2008-11-20 01:20:34', 'elite': '2015,2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.65, 'fans': 58}}
[R11] {'review_id': 'UoQ966EfYIJm5BL7lj0cUw', 'user_id': 'HLgfwU1PWFeln1aI0qWvyw', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Super nice people work here, The only want the customer to be satisfied. Great lattes and baked goods.', 'date': '2021-07-22 12:26:34', 'user': {'name': 'BL', 'review_count': 5, 'yelping_since': '2011-09-30 13:43:33', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.2, 'fans': 0}}
[R12] {'review_id': 'UrtYTH8lfEyJ35CsUDUSEg', 'user_id': 'PkDjBZArSkiOrPzule0I-Q', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I was killing time waiting for my passport at the customs house nearby and went looking for coffee. This adorable little place made me so happy- they have DECAF cold brew! I can't have caffeine and it is so hard to find iced decaf (besides espresso) anywhere. AND they had oat milk. And it was delicious. They had some delicious looking scones and other treats too! Definitely check it out if you're in Old City!", 'date': '2021-07-08 15:42:52', 'user': {'name': 'Lisa', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2017-09-09 20:50:44', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R13] {'review_id': 'jhG2wom9NGQUc83M6YuaNg', 'user_id': 'DrgfjyGIVtjDSPmcDm-oRg', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Totally respecting their in-store customer limit (we love that they're prioritising safety so much), but the matcha and chai we got left us wishing we could spend all day in there! Both drinks were perfect, especially with the use of oat milk. Finding that as an option is always a treat and it really enhanced our drinks. The staff was really courteous and prompt as well, making this possibly our best cafe stop during our trip", 'date': '2021-07-05 16:58:45', 'user': {'name': 'James', 'review_count': 22, 'yelping_since': '2019-03-04 22:22:21', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.74, 'fans': 0}}
[R14] {'review_id': 'nAy5M5ZXcVzkpRzxs38Dgg', 'user_id': 'DDItoaNRmJJYrhJGz4ZJ3w', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': 'We love third wave coffee and always seek out local coffeehouses wherever we go. Menagerie is such a great coffeehouse with a dark rustic feel coming from the brick and natural wood. The service was excellent with them not minding that we arrived ten minutes before closing. We were happy we made it as the espresso drinks were fantastic. Look forward to a return visit next time we are in the area.', 'date': '2021-06-28 20:40:21', 'user': {'name': 'Eugene', 'review_count': 536, 'yelping_since': '2016-04-22 21:41:49', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.56, 'fans': 9}}
[R15] {'review_id': 'sBJ4w59pEMPAKvwkaJgztw', 'user_id': 'gfQqQYI5_hCAGEHlHXIz2Q', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 5, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 4, 'text': 'Cute little spot serving Elixr coffee, which I\'ve enjoyed at their cafe. So on a dog walk recently, we stopped in (well, I stopped in while my husband waited outside with the dogs). Coffee was good, and I was impressed to see that that they have a kitchen with staff making the sandwiches to order. My husband got a breakfast sandwich and I got a pastry. \n\nI get the feeling they might have more food options when things get back to "normal." I\'ll be interested to try those, though they already have some good stuff on offer.\n\nI like that they are open earlier than other spots, so I can stop in when I walk dogs and before things get busy in the neighborhood.', 'date': '2021-06-03 15:28:49', 'user': {'name': 'Cherie', 'review_count': 2113, 'yelping_since': '2005-10-02 00:49:15', 'elite': '2006,2007,2008,2009,2010,2011,2012,2013,2014,2015,2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.81, 'fans': 212}}
[R16] {'review_id': 'Yso-n9TY24UrYTiM-LHKcw', 'user_id': 'TMv2FLijLLr1R92AEoRYPw', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Cute cafe that has adapted fully to COVID. There were no chairs when I went and plexiglass separating the customers from employees.  They work super fast, very friendly, and have still managed to make the place aesthetically pleasing.\nTheir coffee and croissant was delish! \nI wish COVID is gone so I can enjoy an idyllic morning enjoying the cafe to its fullest soon.', 'date': '2021-05-10 17:39:14', 'user': {'name': 'Kate', 'review_count': 162, 'yelping_since': '2013-08-24 23:36:39', 'elite': '2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.14, 'fans': 17}}
[R17] {'review_id': '3n4OQ92ndjvTO7X8Q9_Fyw', 'user_id': 'GtmvDH3LqZf3-NlHUYXgrQ', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Menagerie is the latest on my list of amazing places I have gotten to try outside of my typical Rittenhouse bubble. While I wish I were more of a coffee connoisseur (alas, call it my character flaw), I can definitely tell if coffee is amazing or horrible. Luckily Menagerie's coffee is AMAZING. It is delicious and refreshing. I got the iced oat milk latte and my friend similarly agreed that she loved her cold brew (which is saying something, given how simple cold brew tends to be).\n\nWe grabbed iced drinks from here and roamed amidst the historical buildings. 11/10 would recommend!", 'date': '2021-04-18 19:31:17', 'user': {'name': 'Radhika', 'review_count': 125, 'yelping_since': '2015-05-23 01:12:26', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.91, 'fans': 10}}
[R18] {'review_id': 'GaKZI4xFJKkrUO7tfnJ7qg', 'user_id': 'w48VbOg7VHOxvBg53YGaKQ', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Coffee was ok, not bad, not the best. Breakfast sandwich and donut was very good! Not awesome when your husband waits in line to keep the three person limit and then gets kicked out when a customer comes back in to correct a precious order. These are not cities mandates and customer service should always be a consideration.', 'date': '2021-04-18 16:16:39', 'user': {'name': 'Pauline', 'review_count': 9, 'yelping_since': '2018-09-04 23:53:11', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.33, 'fans': 0}}
[R19] {'review_id': '9peyxlJvDoM2Cb1Ep0oRbQ', 'user_id': 'baYuuCRzwgHn2BAFc7qodA', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Very great coffee and pastries. Loved the Covid-safety protocols in place, felt very safe ordering and inside. We got a latte and a chai, as well as a cute pastry and a slice of Irish soda bread. Both drinks were amazing, the Chai specifically was really good and clearly made in-house. The soda bread was fantastically thick, and they grill-toasted it and buttered it for us. They were also quite fast and very friendly. It's also right near market street so it's easy to get to. Would recommend it as a stop.", 'date': '2021-04-05 13:35:13', 'user': {'name': 'Abby', 'review_count': 255, 'yelping_since': '2016-03-22 23:31:26', 'elite': '20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.19, 'fans': 10}}
