[R22] {'review_id': '1rxbrwZ3PfSr2co-JHf2Xw', 'user_id': 'oJp7znV0fSp0kMMaOuYpsg', 'business_id': '49Gyz-LD9MxTh1yzbYiOhw', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 2, 'text': "Small coffee shop with a selection of pastries, with a small table for 2 outside the door, and handled COVID well - ordered a chocolate croissant, cappuccino, and matcha latte.\n\nHow they're managing COVID: They were very strict on only having 2 people inside the shop at one time, and everyone had to be in masks. Had a screen around the cashier as well, and would pass over drinks & pastries through the screen. \n\nFood: Thought the drinks were well prepared and croissant was very flaky/crisp. However the drinks were ~$5 each, which I thought were a bit on the higher end, given the size of the drinks. \n\nOverall: 4/5 - I do think the prices are a bit higher than your average latte, but they were well made and had tasty pastries! Great job managing COVID too.", 'date': '2021-01-31 21:00:21', 'user': {'name': 'Annie', 'review_count': 138, 'yelping_since': '2019-01-30 15:53:24', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.08, 'fans': 10}}
