It's also cool how they have organized bike rides, and that there's a coffee shop right there! I'll have to try a drink next time I'm there!", 'date': '2017-07-27 02:22:14', 'user': {'name': 'Will', 'review_count': 729, 'yelping_since': '2009-08-02 20:08:27', 'elite': '2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.24, 'fans': 31}}
[R33] {'review_id': '-X9pB4bqFpAhEAQ4NDtlgA', 'user_id': 'r2A6SG_zPp9UGZ_N6hN5zg', 'business_id': 'lTk4efVzepR0PIPayrHojA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "About a year ago I moved across the street from Kayuh and ever since then it's been a part of my daily routine. The coffee is delicious as well as the assortment of other beverages they offer (my favorite being the iced Moroccan mint tea). All of the employees are wonderful, always helping me out with a quick fix of my bike whenever I need it. The owner, Izzy, is the most friendly and welcoming neighbor anyone could ask for! 10/10 recommend stopping by whether you need a tune up on your bike or a coffee to start your day!", 'date': '2017-07-20 15:08:01', 'user': {'name': 'Katie', 'review_count': 3, 'yelping_since': '2016-11-21 03:57:48', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
