[R8] {'review_id': 'HNpypvvngCa4cnTpHpfR0A', 'user_id': 'ju0H1ZlsmczlY8-wkhcWFQ', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'We are visiting Philly for a few days to catch a baseball game and sightseeing.  Looking for Vegan options for me I found Luna Cafe.  I had the avocado toast with tomatoes which was very good and fresh. I also had the plain potatoes.  My husband had bacon and scrambled eggs.  We had a tour planned for later in the morning so we arrived a few mintes before they opened.  They saw we were there and took our drink order.  Our waitress Maddie was wonderful.', 'date': '2021-09-10 18:59:54', 'user': {'name': 'Vivian', 'review_count': 48, 'yelping_since': '2016-11-11 18:38:19', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.92, 'fans': 0}}
[R9] {'review_id': 'MT3P6YXGEYmDLYRXszt6tA', 'user_id': '38Rc2dhSCgtKA85R7EkppQ', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'I would not recommend.  For starters, the food took an inordinate amount of time to come - a fact to which our server was totally indifferent.  She never once asked if everything was ok or if we needed anything.  Then the check came and there was a 20% gratuity automatically added - I would not have given our server 20% for substandard service (maybe the automatically included tip reduces incentive to be on top of things).  As another reviewer commented, there is absolutely no notice of this on their menu (at least not on the menu that you pull up on your phone currently due to Covid).  To me, that is something a restaurant should give patrons full notice of on their menu.  What we ordered was good but I would suggest Red Owl Tavern which has far better service and is only a few blocks away.', 'date': '2021-09-05 23:19:07', 'user': {'name': 'Marni', 'review_count': 4, 'yelping_since': '2021-01-01 22:15:29', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.2, 'fans': 0}}
[R10] {'review_id': 'vlFCSr-spW5Sg6uSLRaIAg', 'user_id': 'NajWj1QS7I2l8dpq8ujyJg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The food was decent but they automatically and without notice add a 20% tip to every order. We were planning to tip but did not appreciate being forced to do so. When compulsory like this, it's no longer a tip. It's just an added tax. This 'policy' is not on the menu, it's not on the website, it's not written on the walls, and the server didn't tell us until after they'd charged our card.", 'date': '2021-08-27 18:57:25', 'user': {'name': 'Liz', 'review_count': 3, 'yelping_since': '2016-08-15 17:29:29', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R11] {'review_id': 'UTu6jkN-itHFg35HIXjfFA', 'user_id': 'JQ_Trfz2RXEKuJ9nVJL3pg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Stopped into this small cafe twice over a weekend Philadelphia trip. The options were plentiful and the quality of the food was good. My only complain was that no one came by to ask if I wanted more coffee in the morning. Otherwise, a solid breakfast spot.', 'date': '2021-08-19 22:12:33', 'user': {'name': 'Matt', 'review_count': 21, 'yelping_since': '2019-02-25 03:58:04', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.57, 'fans': 0}}
[R12] {'review_id': 'IOlietjvWFCEpcQHKyMszA', 'user_id': 'DzxQ8lk0pQwq3kEqTg6sgA', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'We are tourists visiting Philly for the weekend and found this quaint cafe close to our hotel. The place was packed and they had many tables outside as well. The menu has a lot of variety and we ended up choosing the breakfast tacos and chocolate chip pancakes. Both were delicious! We also both got a yummy iced latte since it was so hot outside. The only complaint was that our table was right by the door and the servers and patrons had to keep walking past our table which was slightly annoying but I understand the restaurant itself is very small. Luna Cafe is wonderful and we would come again if we are ever in Philly again.', 'date': '2021-08-17 20:55:11', 'user': {'name': 'Ali', 'review_count': 15, 'yelping_since': '2019-01-08 01:20:45', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.0, 'fans': 1}}
[R13] {'review_id': 'qeKGtnA9qXBq6ooDUMOuOA', 'user_id': 'eTzCYwNp7CEvIWyi0xbLwg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Thoroughly enjoyed my meal, I had the chicken and waffles, my partner had the breakfast tacos, and father-in-law had the Philly breakfast sandwich. Service was pleasant. 20% gratuity made paying easier and honestly the food was delicious. My picture won't do justice being that that I took it after I took one of the two double stack pancakes out for my son. The pancake tasted like it was made like French toast. Very moist and soft. The gravy is a sausage which was normal but the crisp and breading of the chicken it what really knocked it out of the park.", 'date': '2021-08-14 20:35:33', 'user': {'name': 'Matt', 'review_count': 10, 'yelping_since': '2019-07-26 00:53:41', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.91, 'fans': 0}}
[R14] {'review_id': 'XnZvd0KgsbESzBrNu-NBmw', 'user_id': 'MadzA-FMtJpJQogN6xttYQ', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Best chicken and pancakes anywhere!!! Friendly staff and great atmosphere. We love Luna Cafe!', 'date': '2021-08-08 14:39:13', 'user': {'name': 'Brittany', 'review_count': 3, 'yelping_since': '2015-05-18 22:25:44', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R15] {'review_id': '_E2-Bq0trBnl5KiIgjS6lA', 'user_id': 'q8RriCzWf3oMSexlS4UOyQ', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Two days back to back and they still didn't disappoint! They were very busy and the wait for a table for one was about 15min, which isn't bad at all. This time I payed around and had my server make the choice for me, she was a little nervous but I was confident she couldn't mess it up. The hospitality was wonderful and everyone greeted me as they walked past. No one standing still and attending everyone consistently. \n\nThe waitresses choices were spot on, she did cheat a little by giving a sampling of biscuits and gravy (So Happy she did this!). The Breakfast Taco's are exceptionally well done, the chef that runs the kitchen knows exactly what their doing. Pico de Gallo was refreshing and not overly spicy, eggs scrambled to perfection, and the sauce poured over the taco's made them perfection! \n\nNow for the biscuit and gravy sampling, never have I ever had a biscuit like this before! Flaky and perfectly rounded out with a light buttery flavor, the layering makes me think it was made with Filo dough. The sausage gravy richly flavored and had no grit from the sausage. Perfectly seasoned and not overly peppered or salted, most make their gravy greasy and under seasoned, this will not disappoint! \n\nDo Not Miss this spot to have breakfast or brunch! This will make your trip or day and will be back for more.", 'date': '2021-07-24 14:31:01', 'user': {'name': 'E.j.', 'review_count': 10, 'yelping_since': '2018-06-01 22:13:12', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.18, 'fans': 0}}
[R16] {'review_id': 'Y6ZpEECwSaoHh3Bkxx1CrQ', 'user_id': 'q8RriCzWf3oMSexlS4UOyQ', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Stopped by my first cafe in Philly and have to say I'm In Love! The atmosphere is soothing and energetic at the same time. Very friendly staff and exceptionally clean. Nothing like very inviting staff to make the start to your experience a positive one. The iced vanilla late wasn't too sweet and perfect balance espresso, milk, and vanilla sweetener. \n\nNow, the Bagel Breakfast Sandwich! Very fresh Bagel, egg cooked perfectly, bacon crispy, and their Luna sauce.... what the actual f$@&, It makes the experience unique and adds explosive flavor. I have no idea what's in it, but it's a flavor I will come back for before leaving old Philly. \n\nIf you're thinking about going here, stop thinking and just go! You will not be disappointed!!!!", 'date': '2021-07-23 13:44:17', 'user': {'name': 'E.j.', 'review_count': 10, 'yelping_since': '2018-06-01 22:13:12', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.18, 'fans': 0}}
[R17] {'review_id': 'fZ2XjKiqmBpdoi0xhBuPEw', 'user_id': 'E8kVL393yHdGCWVnnx0pgQ', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 2, 'text': 'What a cute place for breakfast! Great food! Awesome coffee and service with a smile.  The breakfast sandwiches are tasty, but I had the pancakes and boom: heaven!   Get there a tad early as they fill up fast with tourist and dwellers alike!', 'date': '2021-07-03 02:20:33', 'user': {'name': 'Stephen', 'review_count': 72, 'yelping_since': '2013-01-03 17:45:56', 'elite': '2021', 'average_stars': 4.51, 'fans': 3}}
[R18] {'review_id': '56ojkEJsqf_IPs_e29KHIw', 'user_id': 'a4oitV8lYoLFVPhDO8k-Pg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Used to be great. Ordered chicken salad online and got a text message it would be ready at 12:25. \n\nShowed up for pickup and they said, "We\'re out of chicken salad." Said, "We tried to call you." Totally lied. My phone did not show any attempt to call. \n\nOffered to make me something else   I said just give me a refund. I called 20 minutes later to see where my refund was. Said, "It takes days to show up." But amazingly a message appeared right afterward saying the amount would be refunded.  \n\n I was hungry and on a tight schedule and every place had long lines.\n\nI\'m hoping the owner sees this and does something about the service. They DO have great chicken salad and muffins...or at least they used to.', 'date': '2021-06-09 17:46:36', 'user': {'name': 'Cathy', 'review_count': 7, 'yelping_since': '2014-03-04 16:29:58', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.86, 'fans': 0}}
[R19] {'review_id': 'Ze5R8qFR3GhN0JvzyfuxQA', 'user_id': 'pBiBhfwTXvNTYJM2EOGPtw', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Had brunch with the family and the food was amazing! We were a party of 6 and were easily accommodated 4 at one table and two at the next which was great for the coziness of this restaurant during a Pandemic comeback. The pancakes were delicious and the oat milk hazelnut latte was sooo good.', 'date': '2021-06-06 03:00:01', 'user': {'name': 'Sherrie', 'review_count': 11, 'yelping_since': '2015-07-27 21:08:06', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.75, 'fans': 1}}
[R20] {'review_id': 'IDKADnBOabVD8GmCAXUR2Q', 'user_id': 'YEtxBUAH_qaqIqce3gl2Sw', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "My wife and I spent a get away weekend in  Philadelphia and wanted breakfast before we left.\nAm I glad we found Luna Cafe! Breakfast was fantastic, the service was great. We initially decided to sit outside but it got a little chilly and asked if we could move inside. I've been to some places and you would think you were asking for the moon, not here it was no bother at all. The next time we visit we will definitely stop by again.", 'date': '2021-05-04 19:32:45', 'user': {'name': 'John', 'review_count': 12, 'yelping_since': '2015-10-01 20:32:38', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.33, 'fans': 0}}
[R21] {'review_id': 'khphJdGDzJ27o9AtxzBLiA', 'user_id': 'dbK2kpRIOAu6o_Yaia7JUw', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Omg I had the avocado toast with egg and it was delicious! This spot gets packed so prepare to wait. From looking at everyone else's plate, everything looks good! It's a must try.", 'date': '2021-05-02 20:43:44', 'user': {'name': 'Alina', 'review_count': 15, 'yelping_since': '2015-09-16 18:21:19', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.73, 'fans': 1}}
[R22] {'review_id': 'LmXs5pvJYVXkdthBi_6Apg', 'user_id': 'z5Xx2a3_B0ZzsYGSDK8yqg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': 'Cutest place! We made a very last-minute reservation, hoping for the best and thankfully they had a spot for us! We had our own little secluded alcove all the way in the back of the restaurant - it felt very safe and we all felt comfortable considering we were dining indoors. The staff was very friendly and accommodating, and the food was delicious! I had yummy french toast and iced chai!', 'date': '2021-03-03 15:21:53', 'user': {'name': 'Sofia', 'review_count': 19, 'yelping_since': '2017-10-30 02:43:51', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.53, 'fans': 0}}
[R23] {'review_id': 'eppyF0DHOUt1BEro7B34ww', 'user_id': 'bNVKNecoSQJ7196xZVzB4g', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Byob brunch! The breakfast bowl is my favorite thing on their menu. I went here with two friends with three bottles of champagne. They have OJ so you can make mimosas and kept our bottles in ice. The staff is very friendly.', 'date': '2021-03-02 11:39:15', 'user': {'name': 'Michelle', 'review_count': 29, 'yelping_since': '2011-04-08 03:22:53', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.17, 'fans': 2}}
[R24] {'review_id': 'iaEUWftFw0MRVb6mOfNnzw', 'user_id': '0CL4UUQUyjUWX8MDg1tgXw', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Love Luna. Go there almost every weekend for breakfast or brunch. Love their breakfast sandwich and their chicken salad! Best Mac and cheese!!', 'date': '2021-03-02 02:44:49', 'user': {'name': 'Abby', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2019-07-22 15:16:45', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R25] {'review_id': 'xMi3zFCSWLLsNfSVnxAyuQ', 'user_id': 'nvKvElggENUequjbSaSJSg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Exceptional, pleasant server, tasty home fries, quick service and very fair prices! This was my first time at Luna Cafe and I would absolutely return and recommend it to many others. We were able sit outside and feel very Covid-safe in a convenient location after they sat us right away without a reservation. Thanks to the gentleman who waited on us for a breakfast that left us SO pleasantly surprised!', 'date': '2021-02-08 18:01:47', 'user': {'name': 'Moira', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2021-02-08 18:01:38', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R26] {'review_id': '-CzURghvd6Z28g9_PDC5LA', 'user_id': 'GD_fG-xPP3jWjvWEpAOcRg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'I had such a pleasant experience at Luna cafe on a recent Saturday morning. Everything from the food to the service happily exceeded my expectations. We were able to sit outside for breakfast, aside a heat lamp and felt that all Covid precautions were taken. Our server was so pleasant and helpful and the food was delicious. Home fries were crispy yet tender on the inside, fresh scrambled eggs cooked perfectly, great turkey sausage and fresh sourdough toast - the ideal breakfast. Can not recommend enough. Will be back soon!', 'date': '2021-02-07 14:15:56', 'user': {'name': 'Erin', 'review_count': 10, 'yelping_since': '2016-06-19 17:45:47', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R27] {'review_id': 'LCPD5XBaekfAXVrfb-egcg', 'user_id': 'cb9zwhihLCfeRNhSEHeJjQ', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Luna Cafe is a GREAT spot for vegetarians and meat eaters alike. They have great outdoor seating set up on the sidewalk, with nice heaters for most of the tables. The staff is really friendly and accommodating - just nice people overall. Their coffees are delicious and the food is always great. I'm partial to their breakfast burrito - it's a great size and comes with crispy potatoes. Their biscuits and gravy is also amazing - the chicken is crisped to perfection. 10/10 recommend to anyone looking for good breakfast in old city.", 'date': '2021-01-17 16:42:11', 'user': {'name': 'Mackenzie', 'review_count': 18, 'yelping_since': '2014-02-08 15:47:16', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.58, 'fans': 0}}
