[R31] {'review_id': 'B0H-ejcvWwPw3muBk1zC4w', 'user_id': 'ZsxdGABDAGQTubiJc8NUWw', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I ordered biscuits and gravy here and it was very disappointing. Biscuits were dry and practically stale. Gravy had an odd flavor and the eggs were not seasoned at all. I'm not sure what their other food or coffee is like, but all I can say is don't get the biscuits and gravy", 'date': '2020-11-08 04:47:37', 'user': {'name': 'Devon', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2020-09-04 15:04:00', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R32] {'review_id': '6hPmpETWCpXd02K__uKyng', 'user_id': '8pQxu8wqOJGKQ-T8_0JbAw', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "We placed our order, after waiting for a while we asked our waitress where is our food.  Waitress tells us the printer ran out of ink, so our order didn't get placed.  My omelette was good, unfortunately my husbands breakfast was rushed and not what he had hoped.", 'date': '2020-10-07 02:56:48', 'user': {'name': 'Christina', 'review_count': 27, 'yelping_since': '2018-02-08 15:36:40', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.56, 'fans': 0}}
[R33] {'review_id': 'bMV-B_K14Kewy5QmMXaUUg', 'user_id': 'XtBjmkF65LCalyx7-pb1Jg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Don't waste your money. They charged for rotten avocado and asked for no potatoes? Best of luck in Covid word I will not be back.", 'date': '2020-10-02 16:48:12', 'user': {'name': 'Peter', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2015-07-20 03:03:30', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R34] {'review_id': 'HS8wNoj6s23NxzwVy9TeGw', 'user_id': 'ejDUqEJu2KWK8SGnrMDu8w', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Luna Cafe has perhaps the BEST breakfast in Old City - great coffee, great pancakes, (especially with banana slices cooked in and real maple syrup), and the breakfast bowl is another hit.  Excellent service, and a great outdoor setup.  Highly recommended!', 'date': '2020-09-25 22:43:18', 'user': {'name': 'Craig', 'review_count': 8, 'yelping_since': '2011-01-31 15:02:20', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.88, 'fans': 0}}
[R35] {'review_id': '_mFd66Qj23uO4Ed1GtJkAQ', 'user_id': 'pnlscR0-0UB3ZORues_Jmg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Found this place while visiting Philly. The waiter was super awesome. The chai tea latte was delicious! The food was great! Would recommend.', 'date': '2020-09-12 00:27:40', 'user': {'name': 'Christina', 'review_count': 43, 'yelping_since': '2012-09-02 23:39:52', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.07, 'fans': 0}}
[R36] {'review_id': 'MCfSOAtHQywyTD8GC7vT8Q', 'user_id': 'ZSxdqJ8O3_-Jcc-EMyDGkg', 'business_id': '7NwFNLC0SwX1SwQYlfF5yw', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "TERRIBLE SERVICE! \nI wanted to enjoy a nice brunch with my boyfriend here & was completely distraught by the time we left. First we ordered 2 of the peanut butter & Nutella smoothies & asked the server how it was made because I wanted one without bananas in it. He said he didn't know how it was made because it's made in the kitchen (whatever that's supposed to mean because if you're a server these are basic things you should know) he also said there wasn't any peanut butter & when I asked the other server he said there wasn't any Nutella. So I was confused about what they had & ordered 2 berry smoothies if there wasn't any peanut butter or if they Couldn't take out the bananas & I asked if he could check with the kitchen first before anything & let us know & he made us pay for everything before we even tried any of what we ordered. We paid & tipped before any of our things came, while everyone else had the opportunity to pay once they were done their meal (there were 3 other tables in front of us that we watched this happen) We got our food & smoothies( we received one smoothie without any Nutella when I never asked for that ) didn't like the smoothies so we asked if they can just give us orange juice in exchange for one smoothie we didn't like, yet they still tried to charge us for one small $4 cup of orange juice. Our tabs total came up to $66 with the tip included & they couldn't give us a complimentary orange juice? I was about to pay for it with my card when my boyfriend tried to take my card because we were just going to leave a $5 bill for the orange juice. The server tried to snatch my card from his hand & I asked to speak to a manager & he insisted he was the manager. We said we weren't going to pay for the orange juice because that was terrible service as paying customers. He also said he was going to charge us for the orange juice anyways without our permission. I will never recommend this place if you are a person of color & I would never come back to this restaurant.", 'date': '2020-08-30 18:40:35', 'user': {'name': 'Janelis', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2018-07-19 17:24:12', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 1.0, 'fans': 0}}
