[R17] {'review_id': '0KqIQcDox5moGN3L64GMPg', 'user_id': 'sUQ7jRJ4TmR7cMx6bjL_GQ', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "This location needs to work on their customer service. They cater to the regulars...one in particular in a fur coat..even when there is a long line. Someone should not be able to walk off the street, just stand by the register and order what they want. They should have to stand in the line like everyone else. It's a common occurrence there and I'm tired of it. Do better. Make everyone stand in line no matter how much they tip.", 'date': '2020-02-28 13:51:21', 'user': {'name': 'Janice', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2013-10-25 18:20:37', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 1.5, 'fans': 0}}
[R18] {'review_id': 'fTSmie0n0igYG3qLe1i7AQ', 'user_id': 'bJgfxs6_h5Tcp5anvdTtYQ', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'I was first introduced to Manhattan Bagel around thirty years ago. Even before Yelp was a thing I wanted to spread the word of these fresh as can be bagels at the age of seven. My family and I introduced the bagel to our family dog and she was probably the most enthusiastic participant I have seen devouring a Manhattan bagel since. \n\nI will continue to preach on about Manhattan Bagel and they really do introduce some quite interesting seasonal items - just look at the picture of there newest creation the Pretzel Pastrami Egg Sandwich I took below!\n\nWhether you choose a toasted or fresh bagel, cream cheese or butter, breakfast meat or delectable fish, I think you will be happy with your experience with this bagel joint I know I was.\n\nAs always people SYOY!!', 'date': '2020-02-02 15:16:03', 'user': {'name': 'Mike', 'review_count': 284, 'yelping_since': '2014-02-25 19:18:40', 'elite': '2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.43, 'fans': 21}}
[R19] {'review_id': 'tdrrxw3EJix8hrk_FU67lw', 'user_id': 'rn_B8ffTR_3ZlW9FcE1n3g', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'I think this place has some of the best bagels in CC. A bunch of funky varieties of bagels and some great cream cheese. I got the jalepeno cheddar bagel, which was really great. My coworker got the lox and thought it was awesome. The staff were super friendly and the prices are definitely fair', 'date': '2019-12-17 16:19:42', 'user': {'name': 'Amelia', 'review_count': 80, 'yelping_since': '2013-11-13 18:11:02', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.77, 'fans': 2}}
[R20] {'review_id': '5aPv4SC_J9pXwV_Ci4TieA', 'user_id': 'Il-3p7UNDQ_dN_XrPhfpLA', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Yum. Wishing I had a manhattan bagel near me. I stopped in before heading to the Made in America Fest this past weekend and grabbed a snapple and two egg bagels with egg and cheese. Hit the spot. \n\nLiked the customer service and the quick in and out food line.', 'date': '2019-12-10 14:39:20', 'user': {'name': 'Amber', 'review_count': 131, 'yelping_since': '2014-02-09 21:17:17', 'elite': '2017,2018,2019', 'average_stars': 4.4, 'fans': 14}}
[R21] {'review_id': 'KB8GE6GikbZyq2RKisyl4w', 'user_id': 'g_xvwFsXufyeBVjNFjruDg', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Love this place. I go almost 3 times a well. Colder is good and easy. The bagels and other sandwiches are delish. The staff is always friendly and kind. The owner is super cool and nice too. I love this place. It has some of the best prices for a quick but really yummy bite in Rittenhouse. I would highly recommend.', 'date': '2019-11-10 18:39:28', 'user': {'name': 'Sophia', 'review_count': 59, 'yelping_since': '2008-10-22 01:50:08', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.42, 'fans': 1}}
[R22] {'review_id': 'rLCTqOzjS9rfNI1zNq5kbw', 'user_id': 'IPBLxqObAk8YFRw6ufbkBg', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I'm easily impressed when it comes to most carb based things. However, when it comes to bagels I am nit picky. Does it taste good toasted? Untoasted? With toppings? Without toppings? Manhattan Bagel checks all those boxes. The only box not checked was the one on my wallet. These bagels cost a pretty penny, but are worth it for a weekend treat. I've had honey whole wheat with honey almond cream cheese and it was delightful. NOTE: they sometimes get the ratio of cream cheese to bagel wrong so be warned! But MAN I can't HATe Them ANd would go back for more BAGELs.", 'date': '2019-09-17 03:24:44', 'user': {'name': 'Nicole', 'review_count': 86, 'yelping_since': '2018-07-31 20:04:04', 'elite': '2021', 'average_stars': 4.04, 'fans': 1}}
[R23] {'review_id': 'xNUaRHU2Sggh5MDPojCScQ', 'user_id': 'C7q2a5wl1bpQqt41fFI5gw', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Omg these bagels are so good. I went here after a night of drinking honestly expecting to get any run of the mill bagel and was thoroughly surprised at how good these were. Not only did it get rid of my hangover but was so delicious as well. The staff was very friendly and helpful. \n\nI dont know what they do to these bagels but I need to figure it out because any bagel sandwich I've had since has left me very disappointed.", 'date': '2019-09-10 16:28:14', 'user': {'name': 'Miguel', 'review_count': 64, 'yelping_since': '2016-01-16 22:53:47', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.85, 'fans': 7}}
[R24] {'review_id': 'n8D6CzOWOBdeBQD8eoHziQ', 'user_id': 'DPfnVtkPdnhPCAAuIEh3qQ', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Really appreciated the help that the guy behind the counter offered in terms of Philadelphia establishments. He went out of his way to get me a fresh iced coffee and iced tea. Would love to come back to try the steak egg and cheese on a bagel.', 'date': '2019-08-09 23:21:50', 'user': {'name': 'Deirdre', 'review_count': 587, 'yelping_since': '2012-10-29 03:37:32', 'elite': '2015,2016,2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.41, 'fans': 48}}
[R25] {'review_id': 'pM4Zu4DQD99Fw2vYuJRp_w', 'user_id': '_EKFAXMBsEoRVn-KcXK2cw', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Bad customer service. After being told my $100 could not be accepted, I kindly left to retrieve an alternate method of paying. Some time while i was gone, they made my order, trusting that i\'d come back. When I got back & up to the register, I asked if my food was cold since I was gone for about 15 minutes or so. The cashier told me "basically, it\'s been sitting around for almost 30 minutes" and refused to make me fresh food, saying that it would hurt business. Not coming back.', 'date': '2019-07-25 15:26:11', 'user': {'name': 'Kelsey', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2019-07-07 12:59:21', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.5, 'fans': 0}}
