[R32] {'review_id': 'LLuydj8MS2EZJ6-OOT28uA', 'user_id': '3vhgB61xMkj5TzBvwzPTMw', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Good bagels around Rittenhouse square. They are super reliable for catering, so I often order from here for events. They have a wide variety of bagel and cream cheese flavors. I haven't had a bagel in store, but I've been pleased with my big orders.", 'date': '2018-11-29 00:07:34', 'user': {'name': 'Nicole', 'review_count': 75, 'yelping_since': '2017-02-19 18:00:40', 'elite': '2018,2019,20,20', 'average_stars': 4.64, 'fans': 9}}
[R33] {'review_id': 'tv4Eq7FkERTmW2HD-c5wCQ', 'user_id': '54e80yq9nBTaDLig4AnusQ', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "This is my third visit to Manhattan bagel, in Philadelphia. Although I am not sure why I go to a Manhattan store in Philadelphia but for some reason it feels right to me. I find the workers here very friendly and talkative, sometimes they look like they're having a bad time and if you say one nice thing they instantly smile in relief... The bagels are great, the sandwiches are great, the coffee is always excellent and fresh, and one of the things I was happy most about. I typically have a bacon egg and cheese on croissant.  Excellent every time. \n\nOpen on holidays but not Starbucks It was open on Thanksgiving morning when Everything in the city was closed due to the parade and the holiday", 'date': '2018-11-22 13:57:03', 'user': {'name': 'Philip', 'review_count': 78, 'yelping_since': '2015-01-17 21:16:15', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.27, 'fans': 2}}
[R34] {'review_id': 'Q3UDMxKgGgIYf46tr8g46w', 'user_id': 'CJDPYGOwZD--9JhcJu3mkw', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Omg I do not understand the level of passive aggressiveness in this place. I stopped in to get three bagels. The woman cut me off after the second one then had someone else get my last bagel. I just said I wanted two toasted and one not toasted. Because she just cut me off and told someone else to help me, she missed that part then just openly talked about me in the most passive aggressive way. Like first off, I'm right here. Second off, just ask if you aren't sure and don't cut me off. There's a ton of bagel places around here and I don't need that kind of attitude.", 'date': '2018-10-01 15:02:21', 'user': {'name': 'Douglas', 'review_count': 44, 'yelping_since': '2012-10-11 17:22:38', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.72, 'fans': 0}}
[R35] {'review_id': 'FMlsLAuPkOK-h4mzKnvbpw', 'user_id': 'PEkKFTgLutmgIXSdRQa1vA', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Stopped by for a breakfast sandwich 2 weeks ago... sausage and egg on an everything bagel... it was sooooo delicious - warm, soft, salty!  The help is a bit abrupt to non-regulars but I'd come back in a heartbeat.", 'date': '2018-09-26 23:41:19', 'user': {'name': 'Janell', 'review_count': 125, 'yelping_since': '2015-08-10 20:47:44', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.91, 'fans': 1}}
[R36] {'review_id': 'jL1hOkUxRbQd6y-6tbNTQw', 'user_id': 'kauJmG3ZiA-m5u0nPrjb4g', 'business_id': 'by2wRASwOKpCZU9KtZ3MHA', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I the only one in the store with two workers, and it was the longest wait. One on the phone and the other doing everything except helping me, it took 5 minutes for someone to take my order, then another 7 to make the sandwich. Lady at checkout made me pay twice because she messed up the amount the first time. Picked the sausage bacon egg and cheese on a croissant. Pretty pricey for the size, but everything tasted good. \n\nWhile someone was in the bathroom, a worker walked by with 2 rolls of toilet paper and realized they were in there with none. She put them on the counter and left, and the other workers let 2 other customers use the restroom without TP even after knowing it was all out. Kind of rude.\n\nCroissant sandwich was alright though, and the cheese made it super tasty. Would've asked for it more toasted if I knew, but alright. Bagels looked average.", 'date': '2018-08-16 20:16:39', 'user': {'name': 'Gloria', 'review_count': 677, 'yelping_since': '2014-06-05 15:44:17', 'elite': '2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.57, 'fans': 30}}
