[R2] {'review_id': 'X-n__N6bvOYiHYWnmKKl_g', 'user_id': 'Dx1WWH_43Is3yaUTBgkj-Q', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "This restaurant is not only a staple in our community; the food is fantastic, too! The owners are both family oriented and kind to the neighbors. Do yourself a favor and visit at least once. I guarantee you'll become a recurring customer.", 'date': '2021-08-30 16:03:15', 'user': {'name': 'Rhonda', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2018-05-04 20:49:43', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R3] {'review_id': '6tdTKmIgQBhe5Nznaj7eTA', 'user_id': 'XXzpZf2uZstsP5v_haO51A', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'This place is a breath of fresh air! As a vegan I can tell you most places have very little I can eat. Some have one or two token vegan items that are not well thought out and not very good. Finos is different. A traditional Pizza shop with the owner right up front, an extensive menu with MANY vegan options. The food is freshly cooked with quality produce and great taste. I love that I can eat at an old school Philly Pizza shop and know that they care about the quality and diversity of their vegan food. Thanks Marco for doing it right!', 'date': '2021-07-20 18:16:27', 'user': {'name': 'Carlton', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2021-07-20 17:48:42', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R4] {'review_id': 'Sa2TICEP04KfpgFjD0Qohg', 'user_id': 'IdxjsFEnYAB9A-tYI48q1A', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Seems like a lot of "New" Mt. Airy folks take issue w the gluten/vegan options here.\n\nPersonally, Finos is the best pizza place in the neighborhood, by far. Seasoned well, great dough and toppings.\n\nThe owner is there everyday and hires guys from the neighborhood.\n\nTell him to take the pizza out a little early and it\'s really really good. Try them out.', 'date': '2021-03-31 00:32:31', 'user': {'name': 'RJ', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2014-09-05 21:32:16', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R5] {'review_id': 'dX6VxCKHm1tTymCQZvX1_Q', 'user_id': 'TJ8Hawan8jDIZHS7AAZJwg', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Not bad for a vegan pizza, loved the crust. Could have used a little more flavor tho for my taste buds.\n\nAlso appreciate the customization and substitution of sauce on a normally white pie.\n\nI do like supporting vegan options, maybe I'll try some of the other ones here another day", 'date': '2021-03-17 19:26:07', 'user': {'name': 'Max', 'review_count': 173, 'yelping_since': '2013-09-04 03:04:17', 'elite': '20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.44, 'fans': 7}}
[R6] {'review_id': '4K0u7_QFRckkg7-NXrZGEQ', 'user_id': 'G5a1VjRDtPHhTSekJ5tNrw', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I can't have gluten and I'm used to the Couch Tomato in Manayunk's homemade gluten free pizza dough. Bought a very expensive gf pie from Fino's and it was weird. No sauce, oily onions, peppers and sausage on a frozen, thin, store-bought gf crust. I think it was like $15. Even though I can walk here from my house, I'd much rather drive 10 mins to Manayunk for a hand made gf dough for several dollars less. Disappointing.", 'date': '2020-12-13 16:44:54', 'user': {'name': 'Lindsey M.', 'review_count': 5, 'yelping_since': '2019-10-21 19:52:21', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.8, 'fans': 0}}
[R7] {'review_id': 'J3scEIAboPTrcL0fX6DTVA', 'user_id': 'EOP0U2jAsJHrAqrU2bXBFg', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I love Fino's , I really don't get the negative reviews, good people always good food .", 'date': '2020-09-05 21:49:44', 'user': {'name': 'Herm', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2018-12-30 17:41:04', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R8] {'review_id': 'o5hOao58Ze_EADEAYBbMxg', 'user_id': '_B0wvp5T0vFZXN2jYHe2Ag', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 4, 'funny': 3, 'cool': 0, 'text': "From my husband who just had this experience at Fino's. \n\nI am disappointed...not in the food, because I didn't get a chance to eat it.  When I went in to pick up my pizza, not a single person was wearing a mask -- during a pandemic.  Even the person who was at the desk to hand over the pizza had a full on conversation with me as though wearing a mask was the furthest thing from his mind.\n\nIt is astounding to me that during a public health crisis where the VERY LEAST you can do is wear a mask to reduce the risk of transmission, nobody there could be bothered.  \n\nNo pizza is worth contracting a deadly disease.  They really should be ashamed of themselves for being so cavalier not only with their own health and the health of the employees, but with the health of their customers.\n\nDon't give them your business until they learn that this pandemic is not a joke.", 'date': '2020-08-22 23:13:37', 'user': {'name': 'Sari', 'review_count': 6, 'yelping_since': '2012-12-27 15:03:11', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R9] {'review_id': '6LnQzH5DGFd77kjcSxRPPw', 'user_id': 'DmfT2HBhi7iJS2zjuP7LHw', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Pizza was actually decent. Thin pizza and cool just right. Have come here a few times now. Though one time it had a lot of garlic on it compared to the others I'd give there pizza compared to other pizza places in the area a 7.5", 'date': '2020-07-27 19:48:08', 'user': {'name': 'Warren', 'review_count': 29, 'yelping_since': '2011-03-22 20:46:27', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.88, 'fans': 2}}
[R10] {'review_id': 'HRk1AjQWbRWJmOQuY-N8EA', 'user_id': 'CAfcYA9WEjeQ_zKT_8YLxg', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I really like the pizza and veggie options at Fino's and have been trying to support them by ordering more often since the pandemic started. That said, I was disappointed when I arrived recently to pick up my order and the men working inside were not wearing masks. The owner has always been really friendly and I want to support them, but I feel like I can't do that safely until they change this practice for the benefit of their customers.", 'date': '2020-07-02 18:38:55', 'user': {'name': 'Christine', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2016-12-21 22:42:25', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R11] {'review_id': 'FTSkM0j9iWkEqhxrI0cujA', 'user_id': 'AabFLAqGWIinwWkpqPGWtQ', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Not sure why all the negative reviews for the vegan options...I've been here twice now in the last month and had a great experience both times.The vegan pizzas I ordered were made with a cashew cheese and were definitely NOT dairy. Both the vegan and cheese pizzas were delicious and the vegan dessert options are amazing. Sweet potato pie is good, the banana pudding is delicious, and the chocolate cake (which the owner threw in for free!) was to die for. \n\nIt's a bit further of a walk than our usual pizza place but we're still going to make it our new spot as the service and food is far more consistent in quality than the other neighborhood pizza place with vegan options.", 'date': '2020-06-30 18:03:23', 'user': {'name': 'Diana', 'review_count': 10, 'yelping_since': '2015-11-27 22:18:03', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.36, 'fans': 0}}
[R12] {'review_id': '2DLHeZVBXBY-suBLnr4IWQ', 'user_id': 'Tok5zBSJdWUhew9rqVHIeA', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'HORRIBLE. Ordered a vegan chicken Stromboli and got a red sauced pepper and onions Stromboli. Also ordered steak fries and got breakfast home fries. When we called the restaurant it was explained to us that they "soak the seitan in buffalo sauce" and then cook it in red sauce. THATS NOT A BUFFALO CHICKEN STROMBOLI. And last time I checked, a side of steak fries didn\'t mesh well with breakfast eggs. The owner would not accept that he messed up. DO NOT GET VEGAN FOOD FROM HERE. Or any food for that matter. You\'re better off burning the money or just eating it.', 'date': '2020-06-28 00:14:41', 'user': {'name': 'Michael', 'review_count': 21, 'yelping_since': '2016-09-17 00:22:41', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.39, 'fans': 0}}
[R13] {'review_id': 'XRskKVXp31S6PRi52-mdsQ', 'user_id': 'EE0hv45Hwt7wScQgIUPC6A', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Just OK is the best I can give, at least on the pizza that we ordered tonight.  They skimped on the toppings and the crust was not completely cooked.', 'date': '2020-06-02 23:39:22', 'user': {'name': 'Ellen', 'review_count': 12, 'yelping_since': '2014-05-08 22:29:15', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.46, 'fans': 0}}
[R14] {'review_id': '6vA7zqWCIsJdLIsCAoYjHg', 'user_id': '7aQL44yElGUDrygwAMIwNA', 'business_id': 'rzOz2hCJmJCe0d0QkMs4wQ', 'stars': 2.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Got roped in by the vegan options but were disappointed.  Vegan buffalo chicken had a little bit of buffalo hot sauce on the bottom of the container and the "chicken" was a nugget of disappointment with poor, mealy texture. The philly style vegan cheese stake was mushrooms and tomato sauce without a sign of fried onions or a vegan cheese.  Wished there was some textured vegetable protein or vegan cheese', 'date': '2020-05-02 23:11:43', 'user': {'name': 'Sophie', 'review_count': 6, 'yelping_since': '2018-08-26 23:08:33', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.5, 'fans': 0}}
