[R7] {'review_id': 'PVwO_Y_q85WBb3rJYwvi7Q', 'user_id': 'qimxTm_J-nNVwOIIpx_u-A', 'business_id': 'YBjFuFJXKBKdsxx2TlQVPw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 12, 'funny': 6, 'cool': 12, 'text': "I more or less stumbled upon Aldo Lamberti Trattoria in Philadelphia's international airport after a flight. During COVID-19 quite a few options are closed so I decided to get some food where I could before my next flight. I'm sure glad I did.\n\nI was skeptical at the food at first, as it's airport food, however don't let that keep you away. The food is delicious and of really good quality. I have gotten some slices of pizza here, both cheese and veggie which were very good. I also have had a eggplant parm stack that was absolutely delicious. The eggplant is spot on. \n\nThe line moves quickly and the people are nice. They have a sanitizing station as well as some condiments towards the end of the line. I absolutely will not hesitate to come here again.", 'date': '2020-12-17 19:35:46', 'user': {'name': 'Joe', 'review_count': 524, 'yelping_since': '2011-07-31 01:55:30', 'elite': '2017,2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.05, 'fans': 53}}
[R8] {'review_id': 'GJwciY4hdtC-G4Uu7_NOdw', 'user_id': 'vMAMQpjrViobfxfkli2I3Q', 'business_id': 'YBjFuFJXKBKdsxx2TlQVPw', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Didn't expect it but, Aldo Lamberti Trattoria was actually extremely good. Cool vibe. Such a wonderful menu, it was simply hard to choose, but I am really happy that I got Chicken Teriyaki. The service was outstanding. They were fast, effective, and got everything right. I can genuinely say Aldo Lamberti Trattoria is amazing.", 'date': '2020-12-12 08:56:23', 'user': {'name': 'Troy', 'review_count': 156, 'yelping_since': '2010-04-13 05:09:44', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.51, 'fans': 3}}
