[R19] {'review_id': 'rJc5RvOmsvxp_B2GdWahvA', 'user_id': 'V25rzYSdc3iAEGsE9IB2Og', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'The Best "Tuna Salad Platter" .. and \nThe  Best "Tuna Salad Hoagie" .. EVER! .. I have eaten both for  over 50 Yrs .. I\'m  Addicted!! ..  their Tuna Salad actually taste like Tuna (very high quality) and is always so Fresh  the salad or hoagie is made as ordered .. to perfection... Absolutely Delicious!', 'date': '2020-12-14 18:04:25', 'user': {'name': 'Josephine', 'review_count': 15, 'yelping_since': '2018-12-22 14:26:17', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.06, 'fans': 0}}
[R20] {'review_id': 'Sq7VUzBqEUf17w22EI3OoQ', 'user_id': '1CfEoXBVlMx7A5LDIhaaHQ', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The driver did not follow delivery instructions. After speaking to him on the phone and responding to his text messages to meet him, he told me he was going back to the store, so I told him to cancel my order. Miraculously, he was able to find my door and left my food outside in the cold. By the time I got it inside, the pizza was cold. In addition, he brought me the wrong soda. I called to talk to the manager about it, as this was 100% not the experience I expected (or the experience I've had in the past), and I was treated to the rudest conversation I've ever had, and told not to order from them again.", 'date': '2020-12-11 22:46:26', 'user': {'name': 'Erik', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2018-03-19 02:41:31', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 1.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R21] {'review_id': 'DLcS1H4a_JV-e8NLn8dCHQ', 'user_id': '_kiWS_j7F1HgM76t759VBg', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Ordered from here last night. Got a white pizza, antipasto salad, and 20 wings.  The food was delivered quickly and was still hot.  Everything was beyond amazing. Wings were a really good size and coated well in the sauce,  but not drowning. Pizza was crispy and fresh.  The salad was amazing. So fresh tasting and packed with a lot of meat and cheese and vegetables.  Was really really happy with this order. Usually never take the time to write reviews- especially to standard pizza places, but this is not your standard pizza place.', 'date': '2020-11-30 08:35:39', 'user': {'name': 'Rachel', 'review_count': 4, 'yelping_since': '2018-01-28 01:16:04', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R22] {'review_id': 'CE_ObIxDyaJdopKQjepqAQ', 'user_id': 'yTF8dNsYLJIDG2cPReFdzg', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Gave this place a shot 2 nights in a row. First night I had the wings-- garlic parmigiana. I must say they are the best  wings I have had in Manayunk. Very meaty and well cooked. Second night it was the Yunker  chicken sandwich. Grilled chicken  with fried onions, long hots, roasted peppers and provolone on a long seeded roll. Next week maybe I try the pizza. Staff was very friendly both times.', 'date': '2020-11-13 00:42:29', 'user': {'name': 'Michael', 'review_count': 76, 'yelping_since': '2016-07-12 19:56:46', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.61, 'fans': 0}}
[R23] {'review_id': 'OjclRf_q1cnm256xSykobg', 'user_id': 'kLkCrafbxLMwMBLMuhvJlw', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Manayunk Pizza is so awesome, I wish I could hang here every single day. I was totally surprised I never noticed it. Every single thing was so delicious and unique, I really loved my Chicken Cutlet Sandwiches. The workers were really pleasant. I can not wait to return to Manayunk Pizza.', 'date': '2020-11-12 03:37:56', 'user': {'name': 'Jason', 'review_count': 158, 'yelping_since': '2020-10-18 18:15:49', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.86, 'fans': 0}}
[R24] {'review_id': 'VDzR8laqKArba1jtEuI3Mw', 'user_id': 'WJu9RMMwJXlnckCxmVim6w', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': "My wife really enjoyed her italian cuts panini last night and the mozzarella sticks and curly fries were standard. Have to say the pizza was disappointing. The crust didn't rise and reminded me a bit of little caesars (not the cheesey bread which is low key the greatest food on earth).", 'date': '2020-10-31 23:55:11', 'user': {'name': 'Ryan', 'review_count': 118, 'yelping_since': '2010-01-12 18:53:02', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.3, 'fans': 1}}
[R25] {'review_id': 'OaHwtsWX2960Mlg0AGTv8w', 'user_id': 'szarX0EALH1HnhDqQ63ptQ', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'We ordered pizza on their website and it was easy-peasy to do. The delivery was right on time and the food was still hot. My daughter had the pesto chicken sandwich, which she thought was delicious. My husband and I thought the veggie pizza was kind of bland and boring. We will probably order again from Manayunk Pizza but will stick to the non-pizza items next time.', 'date': '2020-10-04 16:19:33', 'user': {'name': 'Aviva', 'review_count': 42, 'yelping_since': '2017-05-03 05:52:54', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.07, 'fans': 0}}
[R26] {'review_id': 'qd5HMmNYesFFQ2mchdzjfA', 'user_id': 'rCsgqffVpFcHqHdO2aAHcQ', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 3, 'text': "I ordered the White Chicken Broccoli Pizza and it was delicious! The crust was the best part about the pizza - it was thin, crunchy and flavorful. My only complaint was that the pizza was dry so I wish there was some type of sauce on it but I still enjoyed it. \n\nI'll definitely be ordering from Manayunk Pizza again.", 'date': '2020-09-28 18:18:45', 'user': {'name': 'Natalie', 'review_count': 129, 'yelping_since': '2018-12-15 00:18:47', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.57, 'fans': 3}}
[R27] {'review_id': 'zSo1GfyF2pWwsDqCIKKqcw', 'user_id': 'wjjmZtK8V9-oG-T7-1Op2A', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'About 10 employees working and only 2 wearing masks. Customers waiting with no masks. This is unacceptable during these times.', 'date': '2020-09-25 22:46:26', 'user': {'name': 'Nicole', 'review_count': 43, 'yelping_since': '2016-12-12 22:08:18', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.05, 'fans': 2}}
[R28] {'review_id': 'psEV6liDw8XWql7dMw38aw', 'user_id': 'aU487Da8GLOWONON8YKNmw', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Do not overlook this place! We stopped here because all the other pizza places in manayunk were closed at 9:00. I won't order from anywhere else again. Their thin crust pizza was so thin and crispy, and the cheesesteak was one of the best I have had in a long time!", 'date': '2020-09-12 02:09:35', 'user': {'name': 'Jenni', 'review_count': 23, 'yelping_since': '2010-01-03 02:44:54', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.64, 'fans': 0}}
[R29] {'review_id': 'tJ81eRgR_OwGFQPFW0puGg', 'user_id': 'v7MRFzSjtHgwhNt03LmJug', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Got take-out wings and salad last night: definitely the best wings I've had so far in the city! We've been trying as many different places as we can (I lived in Buffalo for 4 years, so my wings standards are VERY high), and we will definitely be returning! They were quick and reasonably priced; can't wait to try the pizza and the rest of the menu!", 'date': '2020-09-08 16:18:29', 'user': {'name': 'Ashlee', 'review_count': 20, 'yelping_since': '2014-05-14 19:37:16', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.2, 'fans': 0}}
[R30] {'review_id': 'KdfG5e33REAOnpQ0POP6vg', 'user_id': 'W492M91fZvJ2Qu8YviDtVQ', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "This is a quality neighborhood takeout option with really fast delivery.  I've mostly ordered sandwiches, Stromboli, and calzones here and they're always been good.  Anything with roast pork in it will rival if not beat some of the better known sandwich shops around South Philly and Center City.", 'date': '2020-09-08 00:35:16', 'user': {'name': 'William', 'review_count': 21, 'yelping_since': '2015-01-17 19:03:48', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.71, 'fans': 0}}
[R31] {'review_id': 'pzk3ffdGQ5pxsSNl1CTSkQ', 'user_id': 'CUyhM4eGDHqZpFgmJQ4r5w', 'business_id': 's8NjvzYuOefJMCPp_119cQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Wanted some comfort food as I had a rough week so I ordered a pick-up (we are in COVID-19 times). The food was ready before the scheduled time and good and hot! I ordered the grilled veggie hoagie and some cheese fries. The hoagie was delightful! It was very well seasoned and they did a good job at cooking the veggies, chopping them, and still maintaining yummy crispiness. I take time to mention this Bc as a vegetarian, people often just throw non meat things on a bun and tell you to love it. They actually cared how it tasted and I appreciated that. I'll definitely check them out again, perhaps for the pizza. Oh, pick up was easy, safe and clean!", 'date': '2020-09-07 13:39:37', 'user': {'name': 'L', 'review_count': 69, 'yelping_since': '2014-12-22 17:24:41', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.59, 'fans': 4}}
