[R8] {'review_id': '-ZCVj5s830rFoxMWPfU_AQ', 'user_id': 'kauJmG3ZiA-m5u0nPrjb4g', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The chicken on my chicken and falafel platter was cooked perfectly with a little char but a lot of flavor. The rice wasn't anything special, but the amount of hummus, falafel, chicken, and salad you get is a pretty good deal. Pita was warm and soft. The stuffed grape leaves had leaves that were a bit thick, but they tasted pretty average and were bite sized. As a restaurant and corner store, there are a lot of options at reasonable prices, plus they are family owned so I will be supporting this place more often, especially if they keep up the good work!", 'date': '2019-10-17 01:20:03', 'user': {'name': 'Gloria', 'review_count': 677, 'yelping_since': '2014-06-05 15:44:17', 'elite': '2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.57, 'fans': 30}}
[R9] {'review_id': 'Vtvq-lLHM9-i0DjVGYYXSA', 'user_id': 'ZMAHe2llnHN3rzom5GSoAQ', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Love this place- their food pick up is reliable, tasty and consistent. The sisters always are so friendly and easy to check out with. The store has so many healthy options. Discovered that I really like drinking vinegar here. Their produce is also really good, the best grapes always. I like their cookies and the ice cream shop is a summer staple.', 'date': '2019-05-21 22:13:33', 'user': {'name': 'Katie', 'review_count': 14, 'yelping_since': '2015-01-17 16:43:14', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R10] {'review_id': 'WQXw2viStcWx-ZamvgjHRw', 'user_id': 'C7q2a5wl1bpQqt41fFI5gw', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'This place is honestly gross. The chicken was dry and hard. The rice tasted like it was left out to dry and placed in the microwave which removed the rest of the moisture. The hummus was runny and the pitas was like rubber. I honestly took a few bites and had to throw this away. I ordered baklava and they forgot it.', 'date': '2019-04-08 23:45:54', 'user': {'name': 'Miguel', 'review_count': 64, 'yelping_since': '2016-01-16 22:53:47', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.85, 'fans': 7}}
[R11] {'review_id': 'ZHuEgQrbjTkf_TX6VT_hmw', 'user_id': 'bRVikhz5bsvNV33IbpI5JA', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Great corner store that has almost anything you might need. I just try to get in and out as soon as humanly possible, because no matter how short of a visit I make, my hair and clothes end up smelling like their kitchen. Any products I buy smell like the kitchen- like burnt fried food - and every time I touch these items in my house, my hands smell. I try to tuck my hair up into a hat when I dash in. There's got to be something wrong - improper ventilation?", 'date': '2019-03-30 18:50:19', 'user': {'name': 'B.', 'review_count': 5, 'yelping_since': '2014-02-22 17:05:30', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.0, 'fans': 1}}
[R12] {'review_id': 'lVgE1arAiTLcZzaV3FilzQ', 'user_id': 'qCtNRzLetEgm0EzPCXzSJw', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Groceries are so overpriced here compared to other stores! Maybe it's just my experiences, but the Male staff are rude and seem to always suspect you're up to something? Also they keep raising the prices on hot food! Falafel sandwich used to be$2.99!! If it were not for their GREED they'd have a nice lil neighborhood joint we could all come to.", 'date': '2018-12-16 14:02:43', 'user': {'name': 'Dennis', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2018-07-30 12:18:25', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R13] {'review_id': 'a84opV4pgLP3u6kKbsmKqg', 'user_id': '--t1GgwabT-J_6OQG8f5QQ', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Had the vegan shawarma platter. It was quite delicious. Homemade hummus with spicy sauce, cucumber salad, pickled turnips, all great. To have found a place near my house that has tofu shawarma is so wonderful. And the woman who cooks in the back is awesome. \nGrab some dry goods while you're there. I did.", 'date': '2018-10-28 00:11:46', 'user': {'name': 'Shaun', 'review_count': 4, 'yelping_since': '2016-04-26 22:29:50', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.25, 'fans': 0}}
[R14] {'review_id': 'WklOreQx-MdJyFUdMGY5Ag', 'user_id': 'vP2u77abmwF4tL6UIqsgzA', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Local to my residence Liberty Choice market is an amazing resource i could not be without!  From groceries to complete cooked meals, they are great!', 'date': '2018-08-05 15:05:56', 'user': {'name': 'Gary', 'review_count': 52, 'yelping_since': '2014-12-11 00:31:34', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.98, 'fans': 0}}
[R15] {'review_id': 'gS3zZFAZfhM_UYb03EFdyA', 'user_id': 'LhA15JvCCicmpfEsccHEoA', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Amazing! I was a little skeptical after reading the other reviews about the service, but I had a great experience ordering pick up. I was told my food would be ready in 20 minutes and it was already done when I arrived (but was still hot!). When I went to pay, the cashier noticed that one of my items had a price written on it that was a dollar higher than it was supposed to be, so they fixed it accordingly. Not to mention the food was delicious!!!\nI don't know why this place has so many bad reviews about service- the employees were all attentive and respectful, and I didn't have to wait for my food at all.\nMy favorite part was all the vegetarian options on the menu! There were veggie burgers, veggie cheesesteaks, and lots of falafel. There were a bunch of meat alternatives in the freezer section, too. Love this place!", 'date': '2018-06-01 00:20:27', 'user': {'name': 'Sophia', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2016-07-31 19:16:44', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R16] {'review_id': 'ocx88Cre2ZAz-idhzqR43Q', 'user_id': 'bMOTnVsvHkVEzSBlNjUbtw', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I'd have to say I'm impressed by the food coming from a market. I got a random menu in my mailbox awhile ago and stuffed it in my drawer. From all the reviews and taking a look at the menu I decided to go with the falafel platter and the chicken shawarma sandwich. Both were really tasty. The women was super nice on the phone and delivery was really fast. I'll be ordering again.", 'date': '2018-04-21 02:22:09', 'user': {'name': 'Justine', 'review_count': 47, 'yelping_since': '2013-10-09 17:43:56', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.33, 'fans': 5}}
