[R18] {'review_id': 'QpYLBoeYJ0u5u13-QplK3w', 'user_id': 'J_jerijrgPX7CRvG2mMWMw', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'I love having this weird little gem in the neighborhood.\n\nThe staff are friendly and kind, the market is well stocked and has a surprisingly large vegetarian/vegan selection.\n\nThe spicy falafel sandwich is delicious.  SO GOOD SO CHEAP.', 'date': '2018-01-02 22:18:02', 'user': {'name': 'Nicole', 'review_count': 249, 'yelping_since': '2010-09-04 13:02:41', 'elite': '2016,2017,2018,2019', 'average_stars': 3.78, 'fans': 19}}
[R19] {'review_id': 'KPe3pHkkqY0f63bHqe2hKg', 'user_id': 'sjX6nkd7PgojHHsUqd0rdg', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Shwarma is solid - a little on the saltier side but the sauce they use helps offset the saltiness. Price is great and they deliver which is a plus. Only complaint is I wish the customer service were a bit friendlier, I often times find that it's a test of my patience whenever I call in an order.", 'date': '2017-12-21 20:25:14', 'user': {'name': 'Eric', 'review_count': 66, 'yelping_since': '2011-10-25 17:39:27', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.3, 'fans': 0}}
[R20] {'review_id': 'kZgiKnr5LFlz8--7l_T7Tw', 'user_id': 'yPa_4u6hcWEHkziHAeRapw', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Im glad to have this stop near my new home. Ive lived in the area and frequented some in the past couple years.  However, since moving closer to it, and the Berks el station being my new stop Im so glad for this market.\n\nI've noticed with the neighborhood growth, this place is getting better.  The daytime cashier is always super friendly.  Also, their homemade humus is among the best in the city, really.", 'date': '2017-11-30 20:06:31', 'user': {'name': 'Mike', 'review_count': 248, 'yelping_since': '2008-05-08 20:14:06', 'elite': '2009,2010,2013,2014,2015,2016', 'average_stars': 3.85, 'fans': 19}}
[R21] {'review_id': '6uDSNidPia07N7ZaMrD6WQ', 'user_id': 'P7YC-vY40th4OP95FcbfRQ', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Liberty Choice is AMAZING. I can not give it higher praise. I live a few blocks away and have had only good experiences here. \n\nTheir hot foods are incredible -- prices are super reasonable and the food is delicious. A falafel sandwich is $3.99 and an egg & cheese is $2.49. They also have a ton of vegan options. And they are open late! \n\nTheir grocery selection is limited but I have always found everything I needed. They have good sales, and a lot of times they give out free seltzer if it is close to the expiration date. \n\nTheir prepared foods are incredible as well, I love their hummus + their tortellini salads. \n\nSeriously stop in here! There is a ton of seating, both indoors and outdoors, and everyone who works there is kind. You will not be disappointed!', 'date': '2017-11-19 16:55:28', 'user': {'name': 'M', 'review_count': 50, 'yelping_since': '2015-03-19 14:45:53', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.53, 'fans': 0}}
[R22] {'review_id': 'Li-wemKzXIO7lGR4ldClXQ', 'user_id': '9H1-AaAV5KMx_5Z6_XQKvw', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Every time I'm in North Philly I come here and order a spicy falafel. It is next level delicious.", 'date': '2017-09-15 22:23:36', 'user': {'name': 'Nicole', 'review_count': 4, 'yelping_since': '2014-05-11 20:05:03', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.75, 'fans': 0}}
[R23] {'review_id': 'UKjTXcWTajQFmMPnxXnYPA', 'user_id': 'SHdmHa61E-R_R0K1gYLMaQ', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Stopped by here after dropping off a friend for a quick place to eat. A true hidden treasure! I am Middle Eastern and I can verify the chicken shawarma and hummus are amazing! Would definitely return if I am in the area again. Quick service, great food, affordable, and friendly staff.', 'date': '2017-09-05 22:25:48', 'user': {'name': 'D', 'review_count': 13, 'yelping_since': '2017-09-05 22:25:46', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.38, 'fans': 0}}
[R24] {'review_id': 'Mb7WmsDAIrWmJ-55aUcyNQ', 'user_id': 'UoUcF53xTWeGtrycA5A0FA', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Great little market.  I just moved to the area and went in there more out of emergency for something than anything else, and was really pleasantly surprised.  It's inexpensive and they have quite a bit of selection as well as great prepared foods.", 'date': '2017-08-27 23:57:20', 'user': {'name': 'Mike', 'review_count': 17, 'yelping_since': '2015-03-14 19:27:01', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.76, 'fans': 0}}
[R25] {'review_id': 'auk6QJuaYUao4AZxLgEmJA', 'user_id': 'ZwyfgYFlQv0FzRivs5Uvbg', 'business_id': 'JbVtIpb0iKnSzlPT83KMOA', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 5, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'DO NOT EAT HERE!!!!!! This restaurant doesn\'t care about customer service. I ordered a Cheesesteak pizza on the phone. When I picked it up and brought it home, there were no onions or peppers on the pizza. I called the store, and the young woman who worked at the front counter informed me I had a wrong menu. She told me if I brought  the pizza back she would take care of me..\n\nWhen I got back to the store the young lady gave me the updated menu and asked the chef to add onions and peppers. Me, personally if I would have worked there and was in that situation, I would have offered a brand new pizza.\n\n\nWhat does this chef do...he cooks onions and peppers on the grille and puts it into a separate container then gives me the original pizza back. I asked him to at least sprinkle the onions and peppers on the pizza and put it back in the oven.. His response "it\'s sliced already". Then proceeds to look at me like I\'m crazy...\n\nPlease do not give them your business - the way the chef handled this situation was completely unacceptable!!!!! It was as if I bothered the guy!', 'date': '2017-08-20 18:18:03', 'user': {'name': 'Carlyle', 'review_count': 3, 'yelping_since': '2015-10-23 22:39:47', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.0, 'fans': 0}}
