[R1] {'review_id': 'MRSYEsVwe61znu7Q5aONIg', 'user_id': 'FDCQdm8EgEcnTv-dOAYYqQ', 'business_id': 'x1CpCXik31TwTtMPMcrcug', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Stopped by this place to eat twice and twice I left before eating. First attempt to eat here was at 12noon on a Saturday. I was looking forward to eating pasta only to find out they don't serve pasta until 4pm. Mind you, this is not stated anywhere on the website. Second attempt to eat there was on a random Wednesday night and it was closed for a private party. Call it bad luck but this place is not worth the hassle. I shall not be back.", 'date': '2020-02-27 01:33:31', 'user': {'name': 'Noreen', 'review_count': 4, 'yelping_since': '2016-08-24 22:40:20', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R2] {'review_id': 'Wm8dhCgu_a-qFyfo5NZ_rQ', 'user_id': 'HrlJkq3uWBLsiK1NAJOqUg', 'business_id': 'x1CpCXik31TwTtMPMcrcug', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The food is great. So far we have had the pizza and tonight we chose to venture and get mussels. The mussels were great tasting! But... also it \nwas 16 dollars and we had 10 mussels for that order. I don't mind spending the money but was very disappointed in what we got . Decent size but nothing over the top. I've had very big mussels at another restaurant in manayunk and we got about 20 to 25 in that order for about 14 dollars. We definitely we be going back but was hoping for more for the price.", 'date': '2020-02-13 01:01:26', 'user': {'name': 'Maddi', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2020-02-13 00:49:23', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.5, 'fans': 0}}
[R3] {'review_id': 'kASN6SdLnV7mCsCx43Wvbw', 'user_id': 'PV6cmSEG9ADTEptQmxkztA', 'business_id': 'x1CpCXik31TwTtMPMcrcug', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 3, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'We ordered for delivery and each of us had pasta dishes (polpette) and (carbonara). The bacon of the carbonara was served in HUGE pieces that were mostly fat and very tough to eat. Both dishes were fettuccine, the dishes would have been much better done with spaghetti. \n\nThe focaccia bread that came with the meals was good but heavy on the black peppercorn spice. The spinach saltati was ok, but not worth the price. All in all, we were not very impressed with our meals.', 'date': '2019-12-26 02:09:37', 'user': {'name': 'P', 'review_count': 50, 'yelping_since': '2013-11-07 03:14:24', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.64, 'fans': 0}}
[R4] {'review_id': 'w_cuvrwwqEOz50dbJpMcKw', 'user_id': '3VpYwTpNhVS_eqOhCKr5wg', 'business_id': 'x1CpCXik31TwTtMPMcrcug', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 2, 'text': "Such a cute little find at the end of Manayunk / Roxborough. BYOB Italian restaurant with a cafe styled feel. The menu is small but I was able to find something I wanted instantly. The spinach pasta was delicious and the large size white pizza was perfect to split with 3-4 people. The blanco pizza was well seasoned and so cheesy. The service was fast and our server Sarah was so friendly. I'll definitely be back!", 'date': '2019-12-22 02:28:15', 'user': {'name': 'Sarah', 'review_count': 86, 'yelping_since': '2018-04-11 20:40:26', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.01, 'fans': 4}}
