[R17] {'review_id': '2Wc7pPKLqT7_DOaTeABQKQ', 'user_id': 'TLevv568ZCY-8q5rfwPzBg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Fantastic White Spinach and Margherita pizzas. Taste and texture were spot on. I was a bit surprised by how thick the pizza was considering the name Thin & Crispy, but certainly not disappointed. I was expecting paper thin, but it was pretty standard thickness, but it still has a satisfying crispy bite. This is definitely on the go to list for philly pizza spots.', 'date': '2020-07-23 10:57:28', 'user': {'name': 'Marc', 'review_count': 136, 'yelping_since': '2008-08-07 20:35:36', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.51, 'fans': 3}}
[R18] {'review_id': 'AvuuM-okNpgJBxoRG_ij5w', 'user_id': 'XzkAuSae-i9_6Mxe02O41g', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'AMAZING! Their brooklyn pie is absolutely amazing. Perfect crisp, not too thick and not too thin of a crust, and the extra seasoning just make the pie. The sauce on the buffalo tenders is also full of flavor and tastes better than just the average buffalo sauce. Tiramisu is also pretty good. The order came with free garlic knots.', 'date': '2020-06-27 23:13:59', 'user': {'name': 'Reshma', 'review_count': 47, 'yelping_since': '2016-04-24 14:14:36', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.24, 'fans': 1}}
[R19] {'review_id': 'BD9L6tBSGvklaEcX8YGh2Q', 'user_id': '-T2RKUCR_GO0Tclo2RBxzg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'What a great place. Mozzarella sticks to die for. Wings are perfectly crisp and tasty. Sandwiches are full and delicious. This is our new go to for takeout!', 'date': '2020-06-08 01:13:06', 'user': {'name': 'Scott', 'review_count': 2, 'yelping_since': '2011-03-13 02:59:24', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R20] {'review_id': '78MwW56-UEJAqOM2bKD5bg', 'user_id': '9fNFUICoDmtTiz8xVzE1iA', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Exceptional experience from start to finish. The Brooklyn pie is phenomenal. Highly recommend', 'date': '2020-04-09 00:01:44', 'user': {'name': 'Caroline', 'review_count': 10, 'yelping_since': '2012-12-12 02:00:19', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.06, 'fans': 0}}
[R21] {'review_id': '6JnpJVmvtRcLrya0hL5mEQ', 'user_id': 'eWqZ9--L-y4vq8AVP0uvyg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Used to order here a bunch. Sadly they've lost their way by hiring terrible personnel. Counter person Jamie had the worst attitude over the phone. When asked to speak to a manager she handed me to someone who didn't speak English and clearly didn't run the place. Then she attempted to save face after realizing she had made a mistake but went off again after I no longer wanted to give them my business. Too many pizza places in Philly to give your money to people with poor service.", 'date': '2020-01-04 23:21:19', 'user': {'name': 'Kristofer', 'review_count': 29, 'yelping_since': '2013-03-31 21:30:46', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.79, 'fans': 0}}
[R22] {'review_id': 'RX2wu-i2KNCCMFSZIVsJPg', 'user_id': 'jkoQgU0cHqB5j7w0-4ZHPA', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "My favorite pizza place in Fishtown. They have take out only and the owner has been open for two years. Very authentic Italian style pizza. The Sicilian is truly thick and amazing with chunky tomato sauce, high quality cheese and great toppings like sausage and mushrooms. I have used the delivery service and it's only a small up charge and well worth it...and they are speedy. I usually pick it up myself and the owner always gives you a small bag of garlic dough knots for free. I use the Slice app and it is truly the best way. Prices are also very good...just check them out!", 'date': '2019-12-31 23:46:17', 'user': {'name': 'R.Curt', 'review_count': 15, 'yelping_since': '2015-11-07 23:29:56', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.59, 'fans': 0}}
[R23] {'review_id': 'cHejgC_VoemIEMrKZlk4qg', 'user_id': 'UWfzWr4egGzG7Q3_GOT9rg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Ordered takeout. Asked for the special with no spinach. Came with spinach fully baked into the pie so I couldnt even pick it off.  Buffalo chicken cheese steak had close to zero buffalo sauce on it and the bread was a wet all the way through. After spending $40, I was left with a bowl of bland cubed chicken and some garlic knots for dinner.', 'date': '2019-11-14 00:51:08', 'user': {'name': 'Fallonious', 'review_count': 30, 'yelping_since': '2012-03-05 16:58:08', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.68, 'fans': 3}}
[R24] {'review_id': 'IrwYkup-vDscuveYPCEWSw', 'user_id': 'UtXZr255OzYgqIRKtQhEkw', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Total hole in the wall but the pizza is fantastic. I've been living in Florida for the last four years and after having a more than a few pies here I feel like I've moved to heaven. I actually walk past one other pizza joint (pretty good spot) just to get to thin & crispy. True Neapolitan Pizza connoisseurs should walk the extra two blocks to get to thin & crispy. We can tell the difference.", 'date': '2019-10-26 17:32:02', 'user': {'name': 'Mark', 'review_count': 36, 'yelping_since': '2012-02-05 18:00:53', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.77, 'fans': 1}}
[R25] {'review_id': '4PUfgrjgYmzte6zXzi3E2w', 'user_id': 'kauJmG3ZiA-m5u0nPrjb4g', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I walked in to pick up an order and while my order wasn't finished, I enjoyed watching them make the other orders, as I was a little early anyway. The worker apologized a bunch for not being done yet, but once I got my order, I knew why this place had some good ratings! The sandwich I got was loaded with veal parm, and I was able to share it with two people with some satisfaction. The fries were large and covered in toppings. Watching him make the pizzas, I can tell that I want to order one from here at some point! Lovely local joint with some loyal fans!", 'date': '2019-10-09 20:20:06', 'user': {'name': 'Gloria', 'review_count': 677, 'yelping_since': '2014-06-05 15:44:17', 'elite': '2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.57, 'fans': 30}}
[R26] {'review_id': 'qjxP97-8lWc8ktsa5e3VRw', 'user_id': 'JPeqh2XQYSp2h4CJJmwciQ', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Thin and Crispy has the BEST food around, and there are a lot of pizza joints in the area.  The fresh, made from scratch garlic knots are absolutely addictive, and the Brooklyn pizza is so good, we get about 3 of them a week.\n\nThe place is spotlessly clean.  The owner is a very friendly Italian man who treats his employees, well.  I worked for him for a while (only left because I needed more hours) and he was always very sweet and kind.  He NEVER smokes in his store, only outside, I suspect whomever left that bad review was with the competition.  You shouldn't play dirty just to try and get some of his business, your food couldn't possibly be even close to being as good as his.\n\nI work at another pizza show now and I don't eat there, I'm at Thin and Crispy at least a few times a week.  Don't believe the bullshit,  Franco is a sweet guy and he's had employees that have worked with him for 10 years or more, do you really think they'd keep a job where they were treated badly?  I don't think so.\n\nTry Think and Crispy for yourself, their food AND customer service is AAA+++ in my book!", 'date': '2019-10-03 20:00:41', 'user': {'name': 'Lisa', 'review_count': 5, 'yelping_since': '2015-02-16 16:39:55', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R27] {'review_id': 'joX5gkQolKk1-PXXZEg3tQ', 'user_id': '4GP628Cy_QnyEyNkQ9yPTg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Don't know why I waited so long to try this place.  Heard only good things for a while.\nThese moz stix are the real deal. Obviously home made, and so large, very shareable. \nThin and crispy chicken fingers. Pounded white meat, with panko.\nAnd the bacon burger was no joke.\nReasonably priced, quick local delivery, and what seems to be homemade takes on the traditional pizza place stuff.\nCan't wait to try the actual pizza!", 'date': '2019-08-25 23:47:22', 'user': {'name': 'Seanmhair', 'review_count': 26, 'yelping_since': '2011-07-11 18:58:50', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.84, 'fans': 2}}
[R28] {'review_id': 'mcfiLg2m1RukjBMgcK70vA', 'user_id': 'kVQHTSp2YU6Mpka6ZCrPZQ', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Pizza is okay. Not really thin like I expected but is crispy. My pizza was supposed to have caramelized onion on it but didn't. Could have had a little more flavor, like it was missing salt. Did like how they gave two garlic knots for free.", 'date': '2019-08-19 01:50:34', 'user': {'name': 'Justice', 'review_count': 10, 'yelping_since': '2012-08-24 02:26:27', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.5, 'fans': 0}}
[R29] {'review_id': '4RMma0Ejfh19nRiSySZptA', 'user_id': 'jtj9OFPCBLTVWqZL1VbvXg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Great pizza. They are always quick and make great pie. White pie is also delicious. This place is a neighborhood gem. Garlic knots are incredible too. Love their salads with a pizza. This is our go-to spot.', 'date': '2019-08-10 18:04:16', 'user': {'name': 'Adam', 'review_count': 10, 'yelping_since': '2016-10-02 12:05:29', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R30] {'review_id': 'Nw1TtE_HN8eu3jTLDzc1rw', 'user_id': '4rI5Ds1C9qtMhQWCqLmS_w', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 1.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Very disappointed with my pizza order.  There was no description that the pizza was without pizza sauce.  My order was over $40.00 and couldn't enjoy my pizza.  That's a lot of money to waste.", 'date': '2019-08-10 01:09:35', 'user': {'name': 'Iris', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2019-01-11 00:12:38', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 1.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R31] {'review_id': 'Md50Hpf4Oi_HZbIsEOnNqg', 'user_id': 'jxigD0X6vkDDGAFKbFhL8Q', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The best pizza in Philadelphia!! We've tried so many  places and nothing beats the pizza from Thin & Crispy. Highly recommended!", 'date': '2019-08-04 22:45:49', 'user': {'name': 'Juls', 'review_count': 3, 'yelping_since': '2018-03-13 18:12:54', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 2.33, 'fans': 0}}
[R32] {'review_id': 'xM-O8Hi79D70ZPvvsTEmDA', 'user_id': 'ha5jq3G0RMr2wQ0AGnyG4Q', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Wow! Really loved this hidden gem. Pizza was great and priced right. Pickup was quick and easy. The man behind the counter was extremely friendly and kind. He thought he overcooked the pie and was already making another one, but when he opened the box to show me it looked just right (and ended up tasting just right) to me! You have to appreciate establishments that go above and beyond to satisfy their customers.\n\nDefinitely give this place a try if you're in the area! Will quickly become our go-to take out pizza joint!", 'date': '2019-07-29 20:22:50', 'user': {'name': 'Jennifer', 'review_count': 154, 'yelping_since': '2013-09-02 05:00:24', 'elite': '2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 4.4, 'fans': 18}}
[R33] {'review_id': 'Yr46M_XxKzVkIxQSCpsg3Q', 'user_id': 'yCT6OnIKGkR354KfasPUOg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The person that took my order was polite and the delivery was timely. The pizza was ok, definitely not as thin as a thin crust should be and really wasn't very tasty.  So, the hunt continues.\nThe chicken tenders were made fresh and were very good with just the addition of a little salt.", 'date': '2019-07-10 22:45:14', 'user': {'name': 'Kelly', 'review_count': 18, 'yelping_since': '2018-10-07 03:32:25', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.17, 'fans': 0}}
[R34] {'review_id': '4_SAXySp4oL5CDhK0geMnQ', 'user_id': 'oDo9o0oxE3_4U5Q8sPNAmA', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'I really love this place especially because the owner is so hospitable. The food is affordable and delicious! I love the upside down pie! This is a traditional type of pizza that those who are first generation Italians and Sicilians feel nostalgic from. The mozzarella sticks are also so good and huge! They are made fresh! Franco was very welcoming! Those that work there as well are also kind. My hopes is that this small business gets big enough to own a larger property :-)', 'date': '2019-06-21 20:53:46', 'user': {'name': 'Elisabetta', 'review_count': 34, 'yelping_since': '2011-10-23 00:04:51', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.51, 'fans': 3}}
[R35] {'review_id': 'd9IJAVzi0oqKFGbiNLoWYA', 'user_id': 'BnJRHXyU5rsAdLrtcg-GMw', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Was craving some buffalo chicken pizza never ordered from here before but glad I did.  Pizza is really good could use more hot sauce but I'm good after adding a bit of my own.  The crust and everything taste fresh came hot and very fast delivery on a Friday night.  They even sent me free garlic knots so yummy thank you.  I also ordered mozzarella sticks to try and wow never had any like these before they're perfectly crispy and hot and cheesy just what u expect from some very big and filling. I will be ordering again", 'date': '2019-05-11 02:28:14', 'user': {'name': 'Amanda', 'review_count': 23, 'yelping_since': '2013-08-17 17:10:36', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.72, 'fans': 0}}
[R36] {'review_id': 'dCEGMBUXcIWq-DCEMxS4VA', 'user_id': 'Cat17Y3bbanxo1wBV8HrLg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Pizza is excellent. The owner Franco who looks like Robin Williams the older Italian guy is extremely nice and kind.  Love the service and everything about this place.', 'date': '2019-05-01 19:17:24', 'user': {'name': 'Amy', 'review_count': 32, 'yelping_since': '2014-10-04 18:50:53', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R37] {'review_id': 'Mgz2p9XfhUxSuUWYxdU4Zw', 'user_id': 'k0ItOdfAkjrvH7Hj-u7lVg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I was really excited about this pizza after reading a bunch of wonderful reviews. As I was skimming the menu the owner (I think it was the owner) was barking orders at his staff and extremely rude to his delivery driver. It wasn't pleasant to see and his customer service wasn't great either. I have no problem giving money to a reputable owner but I felt a little sad supporting his business after observing how he treated his staff. \n\nI ended up just getting a regular pizza because one was freshly made and looked delicious. I thought the pizza would hold true to the name of the store and actually be thin and crispy. However, it was your average pizza with the average crust that you see on most pizzas. I really enjoyed my pie with some hot sauce but was still turned off by what I had witnessed. Not bad pizza but I likely won't be back.", 'date': '2019-04-28 22:39:22', 'user': {'name': 'Kelsey', 'review_count': 133, 'yelping_since': '2017-11-15 02:04:21', 'elite': '2018,2019,20,20,2021', 'average_stars': 3.9, 'fans': 11}}
[R38] {'review_id': '4R4kE2HDkp9aY7_oH4hNlQ', 'user_id': '6gl5cTB4mqpIbN2pIwD6hA', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Franco the owner not only has quality food but is one of the nicest amd sincere person my husband and I have ever met. His staff goes above and beyond to create the perfect spin for your personal tastebuds. I love my pizza plain with red sauce, not to much not little, just the perfect amount. I also it well done. Not burnt and each and every time its cooked to perfection. We also have has the ziti with ricotta cheese that will dance on your tastebuds. Now most people will say their family recipe for meatballs is the best. I will say this Thin and Crispy pizza has the tatsiest meatballs Ive come across. Living in S.Philly we are spoiled with all the italian rest. in the area  but Thin and Crispy pizza place has stolen our hearts. Its our go to place for italian take out food. Try it, you will not be disappointed! Ty Franco', 'date': '2019-01-03 23:11:07', 'user': {'name': 'Nikki', 'review_count': 1, 'yelping_since': '2016-05-28 00:33:23', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
[R39] {'review_id': 'KrvkLp1tpePmWpIZ0GS7DQ', 'user_id': 'SGTU5pojL8o-UstZqiN4Iw', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I just ordered a pizza from here, a white pie with spinach and tomato, thin and crispy. I got exactly what I ordered and it was out of this world. It even looked pretty :)  they even sent complimentary garlic knots and something new they made, garlic cheese wheels, they were very buttery and cheesy topped with lots of garlic. Delivery came very fast considering that's it's snowing like crazy out there! This is my new place to order from! Give it a try, you won't be disappointed.", 'date': '2018-11-15 20:06:20', 'user': {'name': 'Jeanne', 'review_count': 3, 'yelping_since': '2015-06-25 19:41:13', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 3.67, 'fans': 0}}
[R40] {'review_id': 'A5zWam7HwtED2hxB38C56w', 'user_id': 'MMYlce0L_M65xeh8SwV3WA', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 1, 'text': "Found my new pizza place!! Yess! I've been in fishtown for almost 3 years and tried em all. This is the best, what philly pizza should be like. My husband doesn't really love pizza so we don't order it very often, but he really liked it too. They've easily blown the competition out of the water. Best part was it was such a great price, and the delivery guy was really nice. Also came with the best garlic knot I've ever had for free too! Highly recommend", 'date': '2018-11-13 00:02:43', 'user': {'name': 'Laura', 'review_count': 21, 'yelping_since': '2014-09-22 18:46:00', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 4.1, 'fans': 1}}
[R41] {'review_id': '_s2EoDIElIKrSqIEtFs2hw', 'user_id': 'et_eqWcHKSxuaUAySIaeCg', 'business_id': '3IDTJXyPKz1vOcJQD1Cn9w', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The owner takes great pride in all the food that he makes. There is a review on here talking about him smoking while making a pizza. Franco has never smoked in the shop. Also,you need two hands to make a pizza so it's  impossible to smoke while preparing one. If a pizza doesn't look right after it's baked, Franco won't even send it out!  Besides the pizza, the pasta platters are amazing and are restaurant quality. The portions are enough to feed two people so you can share.He also makes his own chicken tenders. They are really big,fresh and almost\nlook like whole chicken breasts and not at all like tenders. He makes his own mozzarella sticks too. You can tell because they're so big and fat,not like the frozen kind. Sandwiches are really tasty too! His homemade soups,especially the cream soups, are the best!\n I have never gotten anything from there that hasn't been delicious! If you're hungry, call Franco at Thin & Crispy for an amazing meal!", 'date': '2018-11-08 11:24:34', 'user': {'name': 'Barbara', 'review_count': 5, 'yelping_since': '2012-02-03 05:55:55', 'elite': '', 'average_stars': 5.0, 'fans': 0}}
